WEBVTT

00:00:18.894 --> 00:00:20.687
(THEME MUSIC PLAYING)

00:02:06.084 --> 00:02:07.210
EVACUATION OFFICER: We're not clear yet.

00:02:07.377 --> 00:02:09.838
There are still 30 pallets
of cannon shells in C bunker.

00:02:10.005 --> 00:02:13.759
Forget the munitions, there's no time.
Just get everyone on the transports.

00:02:13.842 --> 00:02:16.094
- (DISTANT BOOM)
- Oh, no.

00:02:17.220 --> 00:02:18.597
(DISTANT BOOM)

00:02:28.065 --> 00:02:30.275
We've caught them in the middle
of their evacuation.

00:02:31.193 --> 00:02:34.655
I have my orders from
Supreme Leader Snoke himself.

00:02:34.821 --> 00:02:38.492
This is where we snuff out
the Resistance once and for all.

00:02:39.034 --> 00:02:41.662
Tell Captain Canady
to prime his dreadnought.

00:02:41.828 --> 00:02:47.376
Incinerate their base, destroy their
transports and obliterate their fleet.

00:02:49.252 --> 00:02:51.046
(ALARM BLARING)

00:03:01.223 --> 00:03:02.224
(RADAR BLEEPING)

00:03:02.307 --> 00:03:05.769
General, Resistance ship approaching.
Guns and shields in attack mode.

00:03:06.812 --> 00:03:09.189
A single light fighter.

00:03:16.905 --> 00:03:18.573
(BB-8 CHIRPING NERVOUSLY)

00:03:18.657 --> 00:03:21.034
Happy beeps here, buddy, come on.

00:03:21.201 --> 00:03:22.285
We've pulled crazier stunts than this.

00:03:22.452 --> 00:03:24.496
LEIA: Just for the record,
Commander Dameron,

00:03:24.663 --> 00:03:26.123
I'm with the droid on this one.

00:03:26.289 --> 00:03:28.166
POE: Thank you for your support, General.

00:03:29.334 --> 00:03:30.460
Happy beeps.

00:03:30.544 --> 00:03:31.545
(FLICKS SWITCH)

00:03:31.628 --> 00:03:32.629
Attention.

00:03:32.713 --> 00:03:34.506
This is Commander Poe Dameron
of the Republic fleet,

00:03:34.673 --> 00:03:37.676
I have an urgent
communiquÃ© for General Hugs.

00:03:37.843 --> 00:03:39.219
Patch him through.

00:03:39.511 --> 00:03:42.055
This is General Hux
of the First Order.

00:03:42.514 --> 00:03:44.516
The Republic is no more.

00:03:44.683 --> 00:03:47.936
Your fleet are Rebel scum
and war criminals.

00:03:48.103 --> 00:03:50.564
Tell your precious princess
there will be no terms,

00:03:50.731 --> 00:03:53.233
there will be no surrender.

00:03:54.526 --> 00:03:56.445
POE: Hi, I'm holding for General Hugs.

00:03:56.611 --> 00:03:59.573
This is Hux.
You and your friends are doomed.

00:03:59.740 --> 00:04:02.784
We will wipe your filth
from the galaxy.

00:04:03.702 --> 00:04:05.746
POE: Okay. I'll hold.

00:04:06.455 --> 00:04:07.456
Hello?

00:04:07.789 --> 00:04:10.333
POE: Hello? Yup. I'm still here.

00:04:11.084 --> 00:04:12.794
Can he hear me?

00:04:12.961 --> 00:04:14.212
- POE: Hugs?
- He can.

00:04:14.379 --> 00:04:17.591
POE: With an "H." Skinny guy.
Kinda pasty.

00:04:18.049 --> 00:04:21.094
I can hear you. Can you hear me?

00:04:21.261 --> 00:04:22.804
Look, I can't hold forever.
If you reach him,

00:04:23.221 --> 00:04:26.141
tell him Leia has
an urgent message for him...

00:04:26.308 --> 00:04:28.602
I believe he's tooling with you, sir.

00:04:28.769 --> 00:04:30.520
POE: ...about his mother.

00:04:30.896 --> 00:04:32.397
Open fire!

00:04:32.481 --> 00:04:34.024
- (DISPLAY BLEEPING RAPIDLY)
- BB-8, punch it!

00:04:34.107 --> 00:04:35.400
(BB-8 CHIRPS EXCITEDLY)

00:04:38.695 --> 00:04:39.821
(GRUNTS)

00:04:40.238 --> 00:04:41.239
(BB-8 EXCLAIMING)

00:04:43.909 --> 00:04:45.327
He's going for the dreadnought.

00:04:45.410 --> 00:04:46.411
Ha!

00:04:46.995 --> 00:04:48.121
He's insane.

00:04:50.373 --> 00:04:52.250
Woo-hoo! That's got a kick.

00:05:06.515 --> 00:05:08.391
All right, taking out the cannons now.

00:05:08.475 --> 00:05:09.559
Tallie, start your approach.

00:05:09.643 --> 00:05:10.685
TALLIE: (ON RADIO) Copy that.

00:05:12.270 --> 00:05:15.232
Captain Canady,
why aren't you blasting that puny ship?

00:05:15.649 --> 00:05:18.193
That puny ship is too small
and at too close range.

00:05:18.360 --> 00:05:19.736
We need to scramble our fighters

00:05:20.195 --> 00:05:21.905
five bloody minutes ago.

00:05:22.072 --> 00:05:23.281
He'll never penetrate our armor.

00:05:23.448 --> 00:05:25.242
He's not trying to penetrate our armor.

00:05:25.450 --> 00:05:27.410
He's clearing out our surface cannons.

00:05:29.746 --> 00:05:30.997
One cannon left.

00:05:31.164 --> 00:05:32.499
And here comes the parade.

00:05:36.795 --> 00:05:38.046
(BB-8 CHIRPING NERVOUSLY)

00:05:38.129 --> 00:05:39.130
Yeah! Yeah, I see him!

00:05:44.052 --> 00:05:46.429
- (MACHINERY SPARKING)
- No, no, no. Damn it!

00:05:46.513 --> 00:05:47.848
BB-8, my weapons systems are down.

00:05:48.014 --> 00:05:49.140
We gotta take out that last cannon

00:05:49.307 --> 00:05:50.392
or our bombers are toast.

00:05:50.559 --> 00:05:51.893
Work your magic, buddy.

00:05:51.977 --> 00:05:54.396
(BB-8 CHIRPING)

00:06:03.905 --> 00:06:04.948
(BB-8 CHIRPING NERVOUSLY)

00:06:06.116 --> 00:06:07.117
(BB-8 MOANS)

00:06:07.450 --> 00:06:08.952
Are the auto-cannons primed?

00:06:09.119 --> 00:06:10.120
Primed and ready, sir.

00:06:10.287 --> 00:06:11.496
What are we waiting for?

00:06:11.872 --> 00:06:12.914
Fire on the base!

00:06:17.502 --> 00:06:18.503
Punch it!

00:06:26.887 --> 00:06:29.014
The last transport is in the air.
The evacuation is complete.

00:06:30.015 --> 00:06:31.224
You did it, Poe.

00:06:31.433 --> 00:06:34.644
Now get your squad back here
so we can get out of this place.

00:06:34.728 --> 00:06:35.812
No, General...

00:06:35.896 --> 00:06:37.439
POE: We can do this.
We have the chance

00:06:37.606 --> 00:06:38.690
to take out a dreadnought.

00:06:42.736 --> 00:06:44.321
POE: These things are fleet killers.

00:06:44.487 --> 00:06:45.488
We can't let it get away.

00:06:45.572 --> 00:06:46.740
Disengage now...

00:06:46.907 --> 00:06:49.701
LEIA: Commander. That is an or...

00:06:55.498 --> 00:06:58.627
Wipe that nervous expression
off your face, Threepio.

00:06:59.169 --> 00:07:01.838
Oh. Well, I will certainly try, General.

00:07:02.005 --> 00:07:03.173
Nervous?

00:07:05.967 --> 00:07:07.302
Let's go, BB-8.

00:07:07.469 --> 00:07:08.595
It's now or never!

00:07:08.678 --> 00:07:09.679
(BB-8 CHIRPING)

00:07:17.145 --> 00:07:19.564
(BB-8 SHRIEKING)

00:07:32.285 --> 00:07:34.412
POE: Yes!

00:07:34.663 --> 00:07:36.206
(BB-8 EXCLAIMS SOFTLY)

00:07:36.289 --> 00:07:38.041
All clear! Bring the bombs.

00:07:38.124 --> 00:07:39.125
Captain,

00:07:39.751 --> 00:07:41.544
Resistance bombers approaching.

00:07:41.962 --> 00:07:43.046
Of course they are.

00:07:56.101 --> 00:07:57.477
Bombers, keep that tight formation.

00:07:57.644 --> 00:07:59.688
Fighters, protect the bombers.

00:07:59.854 --> 00:08:01.314
It's not every day we
get a shot at a dreadnought,

00:08:01.398 --> 00:08:02.440
so let's make this count.

00:08:02.565 --> 00:08:03.608
Copy that, Blue Leader.

00:08:03.775 --> 00:08:05.652
BOMBER 1: You get us there,
we'll give it to them.

00:08:05.819 --> 00:08:07.445
- PILOT 1: Copy. We're on it.
- Fighters incoming.

00:08:09.864 --> 00:08:11.408
Gunners, look alive.

00:08:13.576 --> 00:08:14.661
PILOT 2: Snubfighters at two-ten!

00:08:14.744 --> 00:08:15.829
PILOT 3: They're coming in!
PILOT 2: Form up!

00:08:15.912 --> 00:08:17.330
They're everywhere! (YELLS)

00:08:17.706 --> 00:08:18.707
PILOT 4: Here they come.

00:08:18.790 --> 00:08:19.791
PILOT 5: incoming fighters. Form up.

00:08:19.874 --> 00:08:21.251
PILOT 6: Vector in at attack speed.

00:08:21.334 --> 00:08:23.044
PILOT 5: Pull up!
PILOT 7: Flank right.

00:08:24.295 --> 00:08:26.881
PILOT 8: Mayday! Mayday!
Mayday! We're going down!

00:08:27.340 --> 00:08:29.426
Recharge the auto-cannons.

00:08:29.884 --> 00:08:31.594
Target their cruiser.

00:08:36.016 --> 00:08:37.142
(BB-8 CHIRPING)

00:08:37.225 --> 00:08:39.310
I see it. Tallie,
they've targeted the fleet

00:08:39.477 --> 00:08:41.104
and begun the priming sequence.

00:08:41.271 --> 00:08:42.313
Copy that.

00:08:42.480 --> 00:08:43.481
We're almost there.

00:08:44.941 --> 00:08:47.944
Bombardiers, begin your drop sequence.

00:08:54.325 --> 00:08:55.994
BOMBARDIER:
I've got a visual on the target.

00:08:56.161 --> 00:08:58.580
We're approaching the sweet spot.

00:09:00.832 --> 00:09:02.208
- (BLEEPING RAPIDLY)
- BOMBARDIER: Bombs are armed.

00:09:07.005 --> 00:09:08.006
(SCREAMS)

00:09:21.561 --> 00:09:23.605
(BREATHING HEAVILY)

00:09:25.565 --> 00:09:28.151
- Auto-cannons aimed.
- Forty seconds to full charge.

00:09:28.318 --> 00:09:30.695
Destroy that last bomber!

00:09:35.784 --> 00:09:38.495
Paige, come in. We're over the target.

00:09:38.661 --> 00:09:39.788
POE: Why aren't your bay doors open?

00:09:39.954 --> 00:09:42.248
You're the only bomber left.
It's all down to you!

00:09:51.549 --> 00:09:52.967
- Nix!
- POE: Paige!

00:09:53.134 --> 00:09:54.969
Drop the payload now!

00:09:58.723 --> 00:09:59.724
(ACTIVATOR BLEEPING)

00:10:01.893 --> 00:10:02.894
(GRUNTS)

00:10:04.229 --> 00:10:05.313
Look out!

00:10:07.107 --> 00:10:08.358
No!

00:10:08.441 --> 00:10:09.442
(YELLS)

00:10:15.573 --> 00:10:17.408
(GASPS)

00:10:22.997 --> 00:10:23.998
(GRUNTS)

00:10:26.459 --> 00:10:27.460
(GRUNTS)

00:10:29.754 --> 00:10:30.797
(INAUDIBLE)

00:10:30.880 --> 00:10:31.881
(GRUNTS)

00:10:31.965 --> 00:10:33.133
(INAUDIBLE)

00:10:34.092 --> 00:10:35.093
(GRUNTS)

00:10:49.023 --> 00:10:50.233
(GRUNTS)

00:11:01.077 --> 00:11:02.078
(ACTIVATOR BLEEPS)

00:11:10.211 --> 00:11:11.379
Bombs away!

00:11:28.688 --> 00:11:29.814
(EXHALES)

00:11:32.859 --> 00:11:34.485
(ALARM BLARING)

00:11:38.865 --> 00:11:40.992
Direct hit! Dreadnought down!

00:11:41.075 --> 00:11:43.203
(ALL CHEERING)

00:11:46.206 --> 00:11:47.207
(DISPLAY BLEEPS)

00:12:09.604 --> 00:12:10.605
(GROANS)

00:12:15.610 --> 00:12:16.945
FEMALE MONITOR:
General, Supreme Leader Snoke

00:12:17.111 --> 00:12:19.239
is making contact from his ship.

00:12:20.782 --> 00:12:21.783
Excellent.

00:12:22.909 --> 00:12:25.578
I'll take it in my chambers.

00:12:26.329 --> 00:12:28.748
General Hux.

00:12:28.831 --> 00:12:31.834
(INHALES SHAKILY)
Ah, good. Supreme Lea...

00:12:31.918 --> 00:12:32.919
(GRUNTS)

00:12:34.545 --> 00:12:35.588
(BREATHING HEAVILY)

00:12:35.672 --> 00:12:36.923
SNOKE: My disappointment

00:12:37.006 --> 00:12:41.511
in your performance cannot be overstated.

00:12:41.678 --> 00:12:43.846
They can't get away, Supreme Leader.

00:12:44.931 --> 00:12:48.184
We have them tied on the end of a string.

00:12:59.237 --> 00:13:00.363
Rey!

00:13:00.822 --> 00:13:01.823
(GRUNTS)

00:13:01.906 --> 00:13:03.241
(INSTRUMENTS BEEPING)

00:13:10.581 --> 00:13:12.000
(GRUNTS)

00:13:13.459 --> 00:13:15.503
(INDISTINCT PA CHATTER)

00:13:17.005 --> 00:13:18.381
Well done, pal.

00:13:18.464 --> 00:13:20.466
(BB-8 CHIRPING)

00:13:22.135 --> 00:13:25.179
"Finn naked leaking bag"?
What? Did you fry a chip?

00:13:25.430 --> 00:13:26.681
(BB-8 CHIRPING)

00:13:28.683 --> 00:13:30.310
(BB-8 CHIRPING)

00:13:32.562 --> 00:13:34.272
Finn! Finn, buddy.

00:13:35.148 --> 00:13:36.524
It's so good to see you.

00:13:36.691 --> 00:13:37.734
What? Let's...

00:13:37.900 --> 00:13:40.945
We need to get you dressed.
Come on.

00:13:41.112 --> 00:13:42.363
You must have a thousand questions.

00:13:42.530 --> 00:13:43.781
Where's Rey?

00:14:46.761 --> 00:14:48.388
REY: Master Skywalker?

00:15:03.403 --> 00:15:04.404
(DOOR CREAKS)

00:15:12.370 --> 00:15:14.288
Master Skywalker?

00:15:15.915 --> 00:15:17.542
I'm from the Resistance.

00:15:17.708 --> 00:15:20.586
Your sister Leia sent me.
We need your help.

00:15:29.345 --> 00:15:31.055
Hello?

00:15:35.184 --> 00:15:37.061
(SCREECHING)

00:15:38.396 --> 00:15:39.856
(CHITTERING)

00:15:58.833 --> 00:15:59.917
(KNOCKING)

00:16:01.169 --> 00:16:02.295
(KNOCKING)

00:16:02.378 --> 00:16:03.838
Go away.

00:16:09.010 --> 00:16:10.553
(CHEWIE GROWLS)

00:16:10.636 --> 00:16:12.138
Chewie, what are you doing here?

00:16:12.889 --> 00:16:14.223
He said you're coming back with us.

00:16:14.390 --> 00:16:15.391
How did you find me?

00:16:15.558 --> 00:16:17.226
Long story. We'll tell you on the Falcon.

00:16:18.436 --> 00:16:19.812
Falcon?

00:16:20.605 --> 00:16:21.606
(CHEWIE GROWLS SOFTLY)

00:16:22.398 --> 00:16:23.816
LUKE: Wait.

00:16:27.111 --> 00:16:29.030
Where's Han?

00:16:30.907 --> 00:16:32.950
(SNOKE LAUGHING)

00:16:34.118 --> 00:16:37.955
Tied on a string indeed,
General Hux. Well done.

00:16:38.122 --> 00:16:41.334
The Resistance will soon
be in our grasp.

00:16:41.501 --> 00:16:43.711
Thank you, Supreme Leader.

00:16:47.298 --> 00:16:49.342
(SNOKE LAUGHING)

00:16:51.302 --> 00:16:54.138
You wonder why I keep a rabid cur

00:16:54.305 --> 00:16:57.642
in such a place of power?

00:16:57.808 --> 00:17:01.562
A cur's weakness,
properly manipulated,

00:17:01.729 --> 00:17:05.441
can be a sharp tool.

00:17:07.610 --> 00:17:09.278
How's your wound?

00:17:10.488 --> 00:17:11.656
KYLO REN: It's nothing.

00:17:12.406 --> 00:17:13.407
Hmm.

00:17:15.159 --> 00:17:18.704
The mighty Kylo Ren.

00:17:19.622 --> 00:17:21.290
When I found you,

00:17:22.083 --> 00:17:26.045
I saw what all masters live to see.

00:17:26.212 --> 00:17:30.091
Raw, untamed power.

00:17:30.258 --> 00:17:35.680
And beyond that, something truly special.

00:17:36.430 --> 00:17:38.975
The potential of your bloodline.

00:17:39.976 --> 00:17:44.313
A new Vader.

00:17:50.027 --> 00:17:52.572
Now I fear

00:17:54.240 --> 00:17:56.867
I was mistaken.

00:17:59.120 --> 00:18:01.622
I've given everything I have to you.

00:18:02.665 --> 00:18:04.000
To the dark side.

00:18:04.166 --> 00:18:07.086
Take that ridiculous thing off.

00:18:11.757 --> 00:18:13.801
(HELMET HISSING)

00:18:16.262 --> 00:18:20.057
Yes, there it is.

00:18:21.434 --> 00:18:24.895
You have too much
of your father's heart in you,

00:18:24.979 --> 00:18:25.980
young Solo.

00:18:26.188 --> 00:18:27.815
I killed Han Solo.

00:18:29.066 --> 00:18:30.860
When the moment came,
I didn't hesitate.

00:18:31.027 --> 00:18:32.612
And look at you,

00:18:32.695 --> 00:18:35.990
the deed split your spirit to the bone.

00:18:36.157 --> 00:18:38.659
You were unbalanced,

00:18:38.826 --> 00:18:42.538
bested by a girl
who had never held a lightsaber!

00:18:42.705 --> 00:18:43.956
You failed!

00:18:44.040 --> 00:18:45.249
(ZAPPING)

00:18:47.168 --> 00:18:48.544
Skywalker lives.

00:18:49.837 --> 00:18:54.467
The seed of the Jedi Order lives.

00:18:54.634 --> 00:18:56.510
And as long as it does,

00:18:56.677 --> 00:19:00.014
hope lives in the galaxy.

00:19:00.181 --> 00:19:05.436
I thought you would be the one
to snuff it out.

00:19:06.646 --> 00:19:09.690
Alas, you're no Vader.

00:19:10.858 --> 00:19:13.361
You're just a child

00:19:15.279 --> 00:19:17.490
in a mask.

00:19:19.950 --> 00:19:21.369
(EXHALES)

00:19:34.256 --> 00:19:35.257
(GRUNTS)

00:19:42.723 --> 00:19:46.602
(GRUNTING)

00:19:50.272 --> 00:19:51.315
Prepare my ship.

00:19:57.279 --> 00:19:59.031
REY: There's no light
left in Kylo Ren.

00:19:59.990 --> 00:20:01.617
He's only getting stronger.

00:20:01.784 --> 00:20:05.538
The First Order will control
all the major systems within weeks.

00:20:05.705 --> 00:20:07.665
We need your help.

00:20:07.832 --> 00:20:10.459
We need the Jedi Order back.

00:20:12.837 --> 00:20:15.214
We need Luke Skywalker.

00:20:19.009 --> 00:20:21.762
You don't need Luke Skywalker.

00:20:22.596 --> 00:20:23.931
Did you hear a word I just said?

00:20:24.014 --> 00:20:25.015
LUKE: You think what?

00:20:25.182 --> 00:20:29.812
I'm gonna walk out with a laser sword
and face down the whole First Order?

00:20:30.855 --> 00:20:33.649
What did you think
was going to happen here?

00:20:33.733 --> 00:20:34.775
You think that I came

00:20:34.859 --> 00:20:39.029
to the most unfindable place
in the galaxy for no reason at all?

00:20:39.530 --> 00:20:40.948
Go away.

00:20:41.532 --> 00:20:43.325
I'm not leaving without you!

00:21:01.927 --> 00:21:04.138
(BREATHING HEAVILY)

00:21:14.231 --> 00:21:16.692
(CREATURE GROANING)

00:21:27.411 --> 00:21:29.497
(CREATURE WHINNYING)

00:21:51.268 --> 00:21:52.394
Careful!

00:22:06.450 --> 00:22:08.035
(THUNDER RUMBLING)

00:22:28.514 --> 00:22:29.974
LUKE: You're wasting your time.

00:22:45.823 --> 00:22:47.825
(INDISTINCT MURMURING)

00:23:09.555 --> 00:23:11.599
(MURMURING CONTINUES)

00:23:47.635 --> 00:23:49.470
LUKE: Who are you?

00:23:53.223 --> 00:23:55.434
I know this place.

00:24:01.148 --> 00:24:03.859
LUKE: Built a thousand generations ago

00:24:04.610 --> 00:24:06.904
to keep these.

00:24:07.655 --> 00:24:10.282
The original Jedi texts.

00:24:12.618 --> 00:24:17.331
Just like me,
they're the last of the Jedi religion.

00:24:20.876 --> 00:24:22.252
You've seen this place.

00:24:22.419 --> 00:24:24.296
You've seen this island.

00:24:24.880 --> 00:24:26.882
(WHISPERING) Only in dreams.

00:24:28.008 --> 00:24:29.885
Who are you?

00:24:30.260 --> 00:24:31.261
The Resistance sent me.

00:24:31.428 --> 00:24:32.638
They sent you?

00:24:33.055 --> 00:24:35.057
What's special about you?

00:24:36.892 --> 00:24:38.852
- LUKE: Where are you from?
- Nowhere.

00:24:39.353 --> 00:24:41.814
- No one's from nowhere.
- Jakku.

00:24:41.981 --> 00:24:44.775
All right,
that is pretty much nowhere.

00:24:44.942 --> 00:24:47.569
Why are you here, Rey,
from nowhere?

00:24:47.736 --> 00:24:48.779
The Resistance sent me.

00:24:49.989 --> 00:24:51.031
We need your help.

00:24:51.115 --> 00:24:52.199
The First Order's become unstoppable.

00:24:52.366 --> 00:24:54.994
Why are you here?

00:25:07.589 --> 00:25:11.010
Something inside me has always been there.

00:25:13.470 --> 00:25:15.305
But now it's awake.

00:25:17.266 --> 00:25:18.767
And I'm afraid.

00:25:19.977 --> 00:25:21.020
I don't know what it is

00:25:21.729 --> 00:25:23.564
or what to do with it.

00:25:23.731 --> 00:25:25.107
And I need help.

00:25:25.899 --> 00:25:27.985
You need a teacher.

00:25:29.069 --> 00:25:30.237
I can't teach you.

00:25:31.030 --> 00:25:32.072
Why not?

00:25:33.449 --> 00:25:35.409
I've seen your daily routine.
You're not busy.

00:25:35.576 --> 00:25:39.329
I will never train
another generation of Jedi.

00:25:39.747 --> 00:25:41.957
I came to this island to die.

00:25:43.584 --> 00:25:46.670
It's time for the Jedi to end.

00:25:47.504 --> 00:25:48.714
Why?

00:25:49.923 --> 00:25:52.384
Leia sent me here with hope.

00:25:52.551 --> 00:25:55.387
If she was wrong,
she deserves to know why.

00:25:56.472 --> 00:25:57.765
We all do.

00:26:17.493 --> 00:26:18.994
(WHIRRING)

00:26:20.454 --> 00:26:21.455
(EXHALES)

00:26:27.419 --> 00:26:29.421
- You're demoted.
- What? Wait!

00:26:29.588 --> 00:26:31.840
- We took down a dreadnought.
- At what cost?

00:26:32.007 --> 00:26:33.717
You start an attack,
you follow it through.

00:26:33.884 --> 00:26:35.469
Poe, get your head out of your cockpit.

00:26:35.636 --> 00:26:38.680
There are things that you cannot solve

00:26:38.847 --> 00:26:41.767
by jumping in an X-wing
and blowing something up!

00:26:41.934 --> 00:26:43.894
I need you to learn that.

00:26:44.978 --> 00:26:46.772
There were heroes on that mission.

00:26:46.939 --> 00:26:48.398
Dead heroes.

00:26:49.149 --> 00:26:50.567
No leaders.

00:26:55.948 --> 00:26:57.950
We're really nowhere.

00:26:58.117 --> 00:26:59.952
How's Rey gonna find us now?

00:27:02.496 --> 00:27:03.872
A cloaked binary beacon.

00:27:04.039 --> 00:27:05.541
To light her way home.

00:27:07.084 --> 00:27:09.128
All right, so until she gets back,
what's the plan?

00:27:09.294 --> 00:27:11.088
We need to find a new base.

00:27:11.255 --> 00:27:12.297
One with enough power

00:27:12.381 --> 00:27:16.135
to get a distress signal
to our allies scattered in the Outer Rim.

00:27:16.218 --> 00:27:17.719
(ALARM SOUNDING)

00:27:18.053 --> 00:27:19.805
Proximity alert!

00:27:20.097 --> 00:27:21.098
They found us.

00:27:21.265 --> 00:27:22.683
That's impossible.

00:27:35.195 --> 00:27:37.030
POE: That's Snoke's ship.

00:27:37.197 --> 00:27:38.615
You gotta be kidding me.

00:27:39.032 --> 00:27:40.450
- Can we jump to lightspeed?
- CONNIX: We have enough

00:27:40.534 --> 00:27:41.827
fuel resources for just one jump.

00:27:41.994 --> 00:27:43.203
Well, then, do it.
We gotta get out of here.

00:27:43.370 --> 00:27:44.663
Wait.

00:27:45.789 --> 00:27:48.375
They've tracked us through lightspeed.

00:27:49.626 --> 00:27:50.627
That's impossible.

00:27:51.170 --> 00:27:52.171
Yes.

00:27:53.964 --> 00:27:55.632
And they've done it.

00:27:55.716 --> 00:27:56.717
(BB-8 MOANS DEJECTEDLY)

00:27:56.800 --> 00:27:57.843
So if we jump through lightspeed,

00:27:57.926 --> 00:27:59.761
they'll just find us again
and we'll be out of fuel.

00:27:59.845 --> 00:28:00.846
They've got us.

00:28:01.013 --> 00:28:02.764
Not yet, they don't.

00:28:03.098 --> 00:28:05.184
Permission to jump in an X-wing
and blow something up?

00:28:05.267 --> 00:28:06.685
Permission granted.

00:28:06.852 --> 00:28:08.312
Admiral, swing us around!

00:28:08.478 --> 00:28:10.606
ACKBAR: Full astern. Rotate shields!

00:28:10.772 --> 00:28:13.817
RESISTANCE MONITOR:
To your stations! Move, move, move!

00:28:13.901 --> 00:28:15.444
(ALARM BLARING)

00:28:27.664 --> 00:28:28.665
Follow my lead.

00:28:31.293 --> 00:28:33.503
(INDISTINCT CHATTER)

00:28:33.587 --> 00:28:36.131
MALE ANNOUNCER:
Green Squadron to launch position.

00:28:36.298 --> 00:28:38.383
Clear all launch traffic.

00:28:40.886 --> 00:28:41.929
(BB-8 CHIRPING EXCITEDLY)

00:28:42.012 --> 00:28:44.097
Don't wait for me!
Jump in and fire her up!

00:28:44.264 --> 00:28:48.185
FEMALE ANNOUNCER: Technicians,
lock down supplies for launch conditions.

00:28:56.109 --> 00:28:57.819
(MEN YELLING INDISTINCTLY)

00:29:11.291 --> 00:29:12.292
(INSTRUMENT BEEPS)

00:29:19.049 --> 00:29:20.884
Move! Move! (SHRIEKS)

00:29:23.220 --> 00:29:24.888
(GRUNTING)

00:29:24.972 --> 00:29:25.973
(BB-8 SCREECHING)

00:29:26.556 --> 00:29:28.308
(GROANING)

00:29:28.392 --> 00:29:30.018
(ALARM RINGING)

00:29:34.189 --> 00:29:36.441
(BREATHING HEAVILY)

00:29:36.525 --> 00:29:37.567
(BB-8 BLEEPS)

00:29:37.651 --> 00:29:39.027
Poe, are you all right?

00:29:39.194 --> 00:29:41.405
We need to get out of range
of those Star Destroyers.

00:29:41.571 --> 00:29:42.948
ACKBAR: We need to what?

00:29:43.115 --> 00:29:44.491
Full engines ahead.

00:29:44.658 --> 00:29:48.328
Get out of range of the Star Destroyers
and the fighters will fall back.

00:29:48.495 --> 00:29:50.163
ACKBAR: All craft, full engines!

00:29:50.330 --> 00:29:52.374
Concentrate rear shields.

00:30:38.587 --> 00:30:40.088
(RESISTANCE MEMBERS SCREAMING)

00:30:50.849 --> 00:30:52.893
Ren, the Resistance
have pulled out of range.

00:30:53.060 --> 00:30:54.603
We can't cover you at this distance.

00:30:54.770 --> 00:30:57.105
- HUX: Return to the fleet.
- (GRUNTS)

00:30:58.940 --> 00:31:01.360
What is the point of all this

00:31:01.526 --> 00:31:04.905
if we can't blow up three tiny cruisers?

00:31:05.072 --> 00:31:07.074
Well, they're faster and lighter, sir.

00:31:07.240 --> 00:31:09.034
They can't lose us,
but they can keep at a range

00:31:09.201 --> 00:31:11.411
where our cannons are ineffective
against their shields.

00:31:11.953 --> 00:31:14.664
Well, keep up the barrage.

00:31:14.831 --> 00:31:17.334
Let's at least remind them
that we're still here.

00:31:17.501 --> 00:31:18.585
PEAVEY: Very good, sir.

00:31:18.752 --> 00:31:22.172
They won't last long
burning fuel like this.

00:31:22.339 --> 00:31:24.508
It's just a matter of time.

00:32:13.432 --> 00:32:14.641
(INAUDIBLE)

00:32:31.867 --> 00:32:33.910
Move! Out of the way, everybody!
Give room!

00:32:34.035 --> 00:32:36.371
MEDIC: Life signs are weak,
but she's fighting.

00:32:36.705 --> 00:32:37.998
(BEACON PULSATING)

00:33:02.606 --> 00:33:04.357
(CHEWIE GROWLS SOFTLY)

00:33:04.441 --> 00:33:05.692
(PORG COOS)

00:33:10.363 --> 00:33:11.865
- (CHEWIE GROWLS)
- (PORGS SCREECH)

00:33:16.077 --> 00:33:17.412
(PORG CHITTERS INQUISITIVELY)

00:33:23.126 --> 00:33:24.794
(CHEWIE GROWLS ANGRILY)

00:33:27.088 --> 00:33:29.716
(CHEWIE MOANS SOFTLY)

00:34:07.546 --> 00:34:08.588
(R2-D2 BEEPING)

00:34:08.672 --> 00:34:09.673
Artoo?

00:34:10.507 --> 00:34:12.217
- (R2-D2 BEEPING)
- Artoo!

00:34:12.676 --> 00:34:13.843
(R2-D2 BEEPING EXCITEDLY)

00:34:14.010 --> 00:34:15.428
(EXHALES) Yes.

00:34:15.554 --> 00:34:16.972
- (R2-D2 BEEPING EXCITEDLY)
- Yeah, I know.

00:34:17.055 --> 00:34:18.306
(R2-D2 BEEPING ANGRILY)

00:34:18.390 --> 00:34:20.475
Hey, sacred island, watch the language.

00:34:20.934 --> 00:34:22.143
(R2-D2 BEEPS SADLY)

00:34:22.978 --> 00:34:24.980
Old friend.

00:34:25.063 --> 00:34:26.356
(R2-D2 BEEPS DEJECTEDLY)

00:34:26.731 --> 00:34:28.692
I wish I could make you understand.

00:34:29.734 --> 00:34:31.736
But I'm not coming back.

00:34:32.445 --> 00:34:35.782
Nothing can make me
change my mind.

00:34:40.078 --> 00:34:42.581
Years ago, you served my father
in the Clone Wars.

00:34:42.956 --> 00:34:45.500
Now he begs you to help him
in his struggle against the Empire.

00:34:45.667 --> 00:34:47.877
I regret that I am unable to present
my father's request to you in person...

00:34:47.961 --> 00:34:49.254
That was a cheap move.

00:34:49.629 --> 00:34:51.047
...but my ship
has fallen under attack,

00:34:51.214 --> 00:34:53.675
and I'm afraid my mission
to bring you to Alderaan has failed.

00:34:53.800 --> 00:34:55.760
This is our most desperate hour.

00:34:55.927 --> 00:34:57.429
Help me, Obi-Wan Kenobi.

00:34:58.555 --> 00:34:59.764
You're my only hope.

00:35:08.648 --> 00:35:09.649
(GASPS)

00:35:11.151 --> 00:35:13.820
Tomorrow at dawn.

00:35:14.571 --> 00:35:15.864
Three lessons.

00:35:16.031 --> 00:35:18.658
I will teach you the ways of the Jedi

00:35:19.326 --> 00:35:21.077
and why they need to end.

00:35:31.254 --> 00:35:32.547
D'ACY: General Organa,

00:35:33.548 --> 00:35:34.716
Leia,

00:35:34.883 --> 00:35:37.552
is unconscious but recovering.

00:35:38.970 --> 00:35:41.014
That's the only good news I have.

00:35:41.640 --> 00:35:45.935
Admiral Ackbar,
all our leadership, they're gone.

00:35:46.019 --> 00:35:47.062
(ALL MURMURING)

00:35:47.145 --> 00:35:48.980
D'ACY: Leia was the sole survivor
on the bridge.

00:35:49.230 --> 00:35:50.440
C-3PO: Oh, dear. Oh, dear!

00:35:50.607 --> 00:35:54.736
If she were here, she'd say
save your sorrow for after the fight.

00:35:55.904 --> 00:35:56.988
To that end,

00:35:58.031 --> 00:36:01.785
the chain of command is clear
as to who should take her place.

00:36:02.911 --> 00:36:04.579
Vice Admiral Holdo

00:36:04.996 --> 00:36:06.748
of the cruiser Ninka.

00:36:07.832 --> 00:36:09.292
HOLDO: Thank you, Commander.

00:36:15.590 --> 00:36:16.800
Four hundred of us

00:36:16.966 --> 00:36:18.468
on three ships.

00:36:20.011 --> 00:36:22.597
We're the very last
of the Resistance.

00:36:24.599 --> 00:36:26.851
But we're not alone.

00:36:27.018 --> 00:36:29.187
In every corner of the galaxy,

00:36:29.354 --> 00:36:32.148
the downtrodden and oppressed
know our symbol,

00:36:32.440 --> 00:36:34.192
and they put their hope in it.

00:36:34.943 --> 00:36:36.569
We are the spark

00:36:36.653 --> 00:36:40.198
that will light the fire that
will restore the Republic.

00:36:41.241 --> 00:36:45.704
That spark,
this Resistance, must survive.

00:36:46.705 --> 00:36:48.873
That is our mission.

00:36:50.375 --> 00:36:51.626
Now, to your stations.

00:36:54.254 --> 00:36:56.423
And may the Force be with us.

00:36:57.382 --> 00:36:59.384
(INDISTINCT MURMURING)

00:37:02.011 --> 00:37:03.263
That's Admiral Holdo?

00:37:04.264 --> 00:37:06.307
Battle of Chyron Belt Admiral Holdo?

00:37:06.391 --> 00:37:07.767
(SPEAKING ALIEN DIALECT)

00:37:09.686 --> 00:37:10.979
Not what I expected.

00:37:11.187 --> 00:37:12.188
(SPEAKING ALIEN DIALECT)

00:37:12.272 --> 00:37:14.649
POE: Vice Admiral?
Commander Dameron.

00:37:14.816 --> 00:37:17.652
With our current fuel consumption,
there's a very limited amount of time

00:37:17.819 --> 00:37:19.529
that we can stay out of range
of those Star Destroyers.

00:37:19.696 --> 00:37:22.031
Very kind of you
to make me aware.

00:37:22.449 --> 00:37:23.450
Let's get me those fuel projections.

00:37:23.616 --> 00:37:25.827
And we need to shake 'em
before we can find a new base, so,

00:37:25.994 --> 00:37:27.370
what's our plan?

00:37:27.537 --> 00:37:29.330
Our plan, captain?

00:37:30.206 --> 00:37:31.875
Not commander, right?

00:37:32.041 --> 00:37:34.210
Wasn't it Leia's last official act
to demote you

00:37:34.377 --> 00:37:35.712
for your dreadnought plan

00:37:36.421 --> 00:37:38.715
where we lost our entire bombing fleet?

00:37:42.177 --> 00:37:43.470
"Captain." "Commander."

00:37:43.553 --> 00:37:44.679
You can call me whatever you like.

00:37:45.054 --> 00:37:46.681
I just wanna know what's going on.

00:37:47.348 --> 00:37:48.516
Of course you do.

00:37:49.017 --> 00:37:50.018
I understand.

00:37:50.602 --> 00:37:53.521
I've dealt with plenty
of trigger-happy flyboys like you.

00:37:54.022 --> 00:37:55.023
You're impulsive.

00:37:56.900 --> 00:37:58.026
Dangerous.

00:37:59.402 --> 00:38:00.987
And the last thing
we need right now.

00:38:02.030 --> 00:38:05.950
So stick to your post
and follow my orders.

00:38:19.047 --> 00:38:20.882
FEMALE PA ANNOUNCER:
Turbolink banks seven and eight

00:38:20.965 --> 00:38:22.842
are offline due to maintenance.

00:38:23.551 --> 00:38:25.053
(ROSE SOBBING)

00:38:35.396 --> 00:38:36.606
(SNIFFLING)

00:38:56.584 --> 00:38:57.877
ROSE: What are you doing here?

00:38:58.044 --> 00:38:59.420
Hey. Hi.

00:38:59.921 --> 00:39:02.423
Uh, I was...
You know, I was just...

00:39:02.590 --> 00:39:03.842
ROSE: You're Finn!

00:39:04.801 --> 00:39:06.010
The Finn!

00:39:06.469 --> 00:39:08.221
- The Finn?
- Sorry.

00:39:08.596 --> 00:39:10.139
I work behind pipes all day.

00:39:10.598 --> 00:39:14.102
Doing talking with Resistance heroes
is not my forte.

00:39:15.270 --> 00:39:16.479
Doing...

00:39:16.646 --> 00:39:17.772
Doing talking.

00:39:18.940 --> 00:39:20.441
I'm Rose.

00:39:20.817 --> 00:39:21.901
Breathe.

00:39:21.985 --> 00:39:24.112
- (CHUCKLES) Okay.
- Yeah.

00:39:24.279 --> 00:39:27.740
Look, I'm not a Resistance hero,
but it was nice talking to you, Rose.

00:39:31.160 --> 00:39:32.745
May the Force be with you.

00:39:33.746 --> 00:39:36.040
Wow. You, too.

00:39:37.500 --> 00:39:40.420
Okay. But you are a hero.

00:39:41.129 --> 00:39:44.090
You left the First Order,
what you did on the Starkiller Base...

00:39:44.257 --> 00:39:45.717
When we heard about it,
my sister Paige said,

00:39:45.884 --> 00:39:47.427
"Rose, that's a real hero."

00:39:48.094 --> 00:39:49.178
"Know right from wrong

00:39:49.262 --> 00:39:50.847
"and don't run away
when it gets hard," she said.

00:39:51.264 --> 00:39:52.265
- You know...
- (STUN GUN ACTIVATES)

00:39:52.390 --> 00:39:54.100
Just this morning, I've had to stun

00:39:54.183 --> 00:39:56.477
three people trying to
jump ship in this escape pod.

00:39:56.644 --> 00:39:58.730
- What?
- They were running away.

00:39:59.063 --> 00:40:00.231
That's disgraceful.

00:40:01.190 --> 00:40:02.317
I know.

00:40:03.151 --> 00:40:04.152
(STUN GUN DEACTIVATES)

00:40:05.320 --> 00:40:06.321
Anyway, uh...

00:40:06.487 --> 00:40:08.156
Gotta get back to
what I was doing, so...

00:40:08.323 --> 00:40:09.657
What were you doing?

00:40:10.241 --> 00:40:11.451
Uh, just...

00:40:11.534 --> 00:40:13.369
- Doing some checks.
- Checking the escape pods.

00:40:13.536 --> 00:40:15.872
- No, it's routine checks.
- By boarding one

00:40:17.624 --> 00:40:19.042
with a packed bag.

00:40:19.751 --> 00:40:20.752
Okay.

00:40:20.919 --> 00:40:21.920
- Listen, I'm...
- (STUN GUN ACTIVATES)

00:40:22.003 --> 00:40:23.004
- (ZAPS)
- (FINN GRUNTS)

00:40:28.051 --> 00:40:29.052
(BEACON PULSATING)

00:40:35.725 --> 00:40:37.644
FINN: I can't move. I can't move.

00:40:37.810 --> 00:40:39.687
- ROSE: I know.
- What happened?

00:40:39.854 --> 00:40:41.648
I'm taking you to the brig
and turning you in for desertion.

00:40:41.814 --> 00:40:42.941
I was not deserting.

00:40:43.107 --> 00:40:45.360
- I told you that...
- My sister just died

00:40:45.526 --> 00:40:47.111
protecting the fleet.

00:40:47.278 --> 00:40:49.197
And you were running away.

00:40:50.239 --> 00:40:51.366
I'm sorry.

00:40:51.741 --> 00:40:52.742
But this fleet is doomed,

00:40:52.825 --> 00:40:55.078
and if my friend comes back to it,
she's doomed, too.

00:40:55.411 --> 00:40:56.537
I've gotta get this...

00:40:57.997 --> 00:40:59.874
I gotta get this beacon
far away from here.

00:41:00.041 --> 00:41:01.417
Then she'll find me and be safe.

00:41:02.251 --> 00:41:04.128
You're a selfish traitor.

00:41:04.545 --> 00:41:06.297
Look, we can't outrun
the First Order fleet.

00:41:06.464 --> 00:41:07.757
We can jump to lightspeed!

00:41:07.924 --> 00:41:08.925
Well, they can track us
through lightspeed.

00:41:09.550 --> 00:41:10.551
They can track us through lightspeed?

00:41:10.635 --> 00:41:11.636
Yeah.

00:41:11.719 --> 00:41:12.720
They'd just show up
thirty seconds later

00:41:12.804 --> 00:41:13.805
and we'd have
blown a ton of fuel,

00:41:13.888 --> 00:41:16.015
which, by the way,
we're dangerously short on.

00:41:16.683 --> 00:41:18.393
They can track us through lightspeed.

00:41:18.726 --> 00:41:19.727
Yes. And they could...

00:41:20.228 --> 00:41:21.229
I can't feel my teeth.

00:41:21.813 --> 00:41:23.189
What did you shoot me with?

00:41:23.356 --> 00:41:24.357
Active tracking.

00:41:24.524 --> 00:41:25.566
What now?

00:41:26.192 --> 00:41:27.276
Hyperspace tracking is new tech

00:41:27.443 --> 00:41:29.946
but the principle must be
the same as any active tracker.

00:41:30.113 --> 00:41:31.698
- They're only tracking us...
- Only tracking us...

00:41:31.864 --> 00:41:33.157
BOTH: ...from the lead ship.

00:41:33.324 --> 00:41:34.701
But we can't get to the tracker.

00:41:34.784 --> 00:41:36.911
It's an A-class process,
they'll control it from the main bridge.

00:41:36.995 --> 00:41:38.329
Well, I mean, yes,
but every A-class process...

00:41:38.496 --> 00:41:40.873
BOTH: ...has a dedicated power breaker.

00:41:41.416 --> 00:41:43.876
But... Wait, but who knows
where the breaker room

00:41:43.960 --> 00:41:44.961
is on a Star Destroyer?

00:41:47.255 --> 00:41:49.132
I'm the guy that used to mop it.

00:41:49.590 --> 00:41:50.842
If I can get us there,

00:41:51.300 --> 00:41:53.177
I can shut their tracker down.

00:41:53.678 --> 00:41:55.638
Just give it to me
one more time, simpler.

00:41:55.805 --> 00:41:59.100
So, the First Order's only tracking us
from one Destroyer, the lead one.

00:41:59.267 --> 00:42:00.351
So we blow that one up?

00:42:00.518 --> 00:42:01.728
I like where your head's at, but no.

00:42:01.894 --> 00:42:03.604
They'd only start tracking us
from another Destroyer.

00:42:03.730 --> 00:42:04.731
ROSE: But if we can...

00:42:04.814 --> 00:42:06.983
If we sneak on board the lead Destroyer
and disable the tracker

00:42:07.066 --> 00:42:08.276
without them realizing, then we can...

00:42:08.443 --> 00:42:10.528
They won't realize it's off
for one system cycle.

00:42:10.695 --> 00:42:13.072
- About six minutes.
- FINN: Sneak on board.

00:42:15.408 --> 00:42:16.909
Disable the tracker.

00:42:18.327 --> 00:42:20.538
Our fleet escapes before they realize.

00:42:22.915 --> 00:42:23.916
Hmm.

00:42:28.921 --> 00:42:29.922
How'd you two meet?

00:42:32.884 --> 00:42:33.885
Just luck.

00:42:35.636 --> 00:42:36.721
POE: Yeah?

00:42:37.013 --> 00:42:38.222
Good luck?

00:42:38.681 --> 00:42:39.849
Not sure yet.

00:42:40.308 --> 00:42:41.684
Poe, we gotta do this.

00:42:41.851 --> 00:42:44.020
It'll save the fleet and it'll save Rey.

00:42:45.813 --> 00:42:48.357
C-3PO: If I must be
the sole voice of reason,

00:42:48.524 --> 00:42:50.526
Admiral Holdo will never
agree to this plan.

00:42:51.861 --> 00:42:54.322
Yeah, you're right, Threepio.

00:42:54.489 --> 00:42:57.033
It's a "need-to-know" plan,
and she doesn't.

00:42:57.200 --> 00:42:58.826
- That wasn't exactly my...
- All right,

00:42:58.993 --> 00:43:00.369
you guys shut down that tracker.

00:43:00.536 --> 00:43:01.996
I'll be here to jump us to lightspeed.

00:43:02.163 --> 00:43:03.164
The question is,

00:43:03.331 --> 00:43:05.374
how do we sneak the two of you
onto Snoke's Destroyer?

00:43:05.541 --> 00:43:06.542
ROSE: We steal clearance codes.

00:43:06.709 --> 00:43:08.628
No, they're bio-hexacrypt
and rescrambled every hour.

00:43:10.546 --> 00:43:13.132
We can't get through their
security shields undetected.

00:43:13.800 --> 00:43:15.051
Nobody can.

00:43:18.888 --> 00:43:20.389
Could I do it?

00:43:20.556 --> 00:43:22.809
Of course I could do it.
But I can't do it.

00:43:23.142 --> 00:43:24.852
I'm a little tied down right now.

00:43:24.936 --> 00:43:26.187
- (BLASTER FIRING)
- C-3PO: Oh!

00:43:26.270 --> 00:43:28.189
FINN: Maz? What is happening?

00:43:28.272 --> 00:43:31.651
Union dispute. You do not want
to hear about it. (GRUNTS)

00:43:31.734 --> 00:43:33.486
But, lucky for you,

00:43:33.653 --> 00:43:37.406
there's exactly one guy I trust
who can crack that kind of security!

00:43:37.490 --> 00:43:38.991
- (BLASTERS FIRING)
- (MAZ GRUNTS)

00:43:39.867 --> 00:43:41.536
He's a master codebreaker,

00:43:41.702 --> 00:43:44.705
an ace pilot,
a poet with a blaster.

00:43:44.789 --> 00:43:46.165
(GRUNTING)

00:43:47.333 --> 00:43:48.334
C-3PO: Oh, my.

00:43:48.501 --> 00:43:50.753
It sounds like this codebreaker fellow
can do everything.

00:43:50.920 --> 00:43:53.381
Oh, yes, he can.

00:43:54.799 --> 00:43:58.761
You'll find him with a red
plom bloom on his lapel

00:43:58.928 --> 00:44:01.514
rolling at a high stakes table

00:44:01.889 --> 00:44:03.891
in the casino on Canto Bight.

00:44:04.058 --> 00:44:07.019
Canto Bight? No, no. That's... Maz...

00:44:07.186 --> 00:44:09.021
Is there any way that we can
take care of this ourselves?

00:44:09.188 --> 00:44:11.899
Sorry, kiddo.
This is rarefied cracking.

00:44:12.400 --> 00:44:13.776
You wanna get on that Destroyer,

00:44:13.860 --> 00:44:15.403
I only know one option.

00:44:15.903 --> 00:44:18.447
Find the Master Codebreaker.

00:44:20.074 --> 00:44:21.075
(POE SIGHS)

00:44:21.784 --> 00:44:23.119
(BEACON PULSATING)

00:45:17.715 --> 00:45:18.966
- (BLASTER FIRING)
- (GRUNTS)

00:45:36.609 --> 00:45:38.027
(MOUSE DROID BLEEPING)

00:45:46.744 --> 00:45:49.163
You'll bring Luke Skywalker to me.

00:45:55.378 --> 00:45:57.630
You're not doing this.
The effort would kill you.

00:46:02.635 --> 00:46:03.719
Can you see my surroundings?

00:46:03.886 --> 00:46:05.388
You're gonna pay for what you did!

00:46:05.554 --> 00:46:06.847
I can't see yours.

00:46:08.516 --> 00:46:09.725
Just you.

00:46:11.978 --> 00:46:13.354
So, no.

00:46:14.981 --> 00:46:17.358
This is something else.

00:46:17.441 --> 00:46:18.734
(DOOR OPENING)

00:46:23.322 --> 00:46:24.323
Luke.

00:46:24.699 --> 00:46:26.450
What's that about?

00:46:29.161 --> 00:46:31.205
(SPEAKING ALIEN DIALECT)

00:46:41.048 --> 00:46:43.426
I was cleaning my blaster.
It went off.

00:46:46.470 --> 00:46:47.638
LUKE: Let's get started.

00:46:47.722 --> 00:46:49.724
(SPEAKING ALIEN DIALECT)

00:46:51.809 --> 00:46:53.269
Who were those things?

00:46:54.061 --> 00:46:55.396
Caretakers.

00:46:55.563 --> 00:46:56.689
Island natives.

00:46:56.856 --> 00:46:59.233
They've kept up the Jedi structures
since they were built.

00:46:59.942 --> 00:47:01.527
I don't think they like me.

00:47:01.694 --> 00:47:03.362
LUKE: Can't imagine why.

00:47:39.315 --> 00:47:40.649
REY: Master Skywalker,

00:47:41.150 --> 00:47:42.318
we need you to bring the Jedi back

00:47:42.485 --> 00:47:45.279
because Kylo Ren is strong
with the dark side of the Force.

00:47:45.446 --> 00:47:47.907
Without the Jedi, we won't
stand a chance against him.

00:47:48.074 --> 00:47:50.409
What do you know
about the Force?

00:47:50.910 --> 00:47:53.746
It's a power that Jedi have
that lets them control people

00:47:54.497 --> 00:47:55.915
and make things float.

00:47:55.998 --> 00:47:56.999
LUKE: Impressive.

00:47:57.166 --> 00:47:59.126
Every word in that sentence was wrong.

00:47:59.627 --> 00:48:02.880
Lesson one, sit here, legs crossed.

00:48:09.720 --> 00:48:12.807
The Force is not a power you have.

00:48:12.973 --> 00:48:15.267
It's not about lifting rocks.

00:48:15.643 --> 00:48:17.478
It's the energy between all things,

00:48:17.645 --> 00:48:19.730
a tension, a balance,

00:48:19.897 --> 00:48:22.149
that binds the universe together.

00:48:22.316 --> 00:48:23.317
Okay.

00:48:24.485 --> 00:48:25.653
But what is it?

00:48:27.113 --> 00:48:28.322
Close your eyes.

00:48:30.241 --> 00:48:31.617
Breathe.

00:48:32.326 --> 00:48:33.327
Now,

00:48:34.745 --> 00:48:35.913
reach out.

00:48:42.670 --> 00:48:43.712
(GASPS) I feel something.

00:48:43.838 --> 00:48:44.839
- You feel it?
- Yes, I feel it.

00:48:44.922 --> 00:48:45.923
- That's the Force.
- Really?

00:48:46.090 --> 00:48:47.550
LUKE: Wow, it must be
really strong with you.

00:48:47.716 --> 00:48:48.717
I've never felt any...

00:48:48.884 --> 00:48:49.885
Ow!

00:48:52.721 --> 00:48:53.973
You meant reach out like...

00:48:56.600 --> 00:48:57.601
I'll try again.

00:49:00.104 --> 00:49:01.105
LUKE: Breathe.

00:49:03.357 --> 00:49:05.234
Just breathe.

00:49:08.404 --> 00:49:10.656
Reach out with your feelings.

00:49:15.995 --> 00:49:17.204
What do you see?

00:49:21.292 --> 00:49:22.293
REY: The island.

00:49:24.211 --> 00:49:25.254
Life.

00:49:26.589 --> 00:49:27.923
Death and decay,

00:49:29.467 --> 00:49:30.926
that feeds new life.

00:49:32.595 --> 00:49:33.637
Warmth.

00:49:34.763 --> 00:49:35.764
Cold.

00:49:38.058 --> 00:49:39.435
Peace.

00:49:41.020 --> 00:49:42.313
Violence.

00:49:43.355 --> 00:49:44.857
And between it all?

00:49:45.649 --> 00:49:46.650
Balance.

00:49:47.401 --> 00:49:48.652
An energy.

00:49:51.822 --> 00:49:53.282
A Force.

00:49:54.909 --> 00:49:56.535
And inside you?

00:49:57.661 --> 00:49:59.288
Inside me

00:50:00.456 --> 00:50:02.500
that same Force.

00:50:04.001 --> 00:50:06.795
And this is the lesson.

00:50:06.962 --> 00:50:10.090
That Force does not
belong to the Jedi.

00:50:11.342 --> 00:50:14.136
To say that if the Jedi die,
the light dies, is vanity.

00:50:14.303 --> 00:50:16.430
Can you feel that?

00:50:18.182 --> 00:50:19.850
There's something else

00:50:21.894 --> 00:50:23.312
beneath the island.

00:50:24.230 --> 00:50:25.231
A place.

00:50:26.607 --> 00:50:27.775
A dark place.

00:50:29.860 --> 00:50:30.986
Balance.

00:50:31.779 --> 00:50:33.614
Powerful light, powerful darkness.

00:50:33.948 --> 00:50:35.074
It's cold.

00:50:40.829 --> 00:50:41.914
It's calling me.

00:50:43.249 --> 00:50:44.291
Resist it, Rey.

00:50:45.417 --> 00:50:46.585
Rey?

00:50:49.213 --> 00:50:50.214
Rey!

00:50:53.634 --> 00:50:54.969
(ROARING)

00:50:56.387 --> 00:50:58.430
(PANTING)

00:50:59.056 --> 00:51:00.849
You went straight to the dark.

00:51:02.184 --> 00:51:03.769
That place was trying
to show me something.

00:51:03.936 --> 00:51:05.771
It offered something you needed.

00:51:06.355 --> 00:51:08.691
And you didn't even try
to stop yourself.

00:51:09.858 --> 00:51:11.443
REY: But I didn't see you.

00:51:13.404 --> 00:51:15.072
Nothing from you.

00:51:18.534 --> 00:51:20.828
You've closed yourself off
from the Force.

00:51:24.415 --> 00:51:25.749
Of course you have.

00:51:27.126 --> 00:51:30.212
I've seen this raw strength
only once before,

00:51:30.713 --> 00:51:32.464
in Ben Solo.

00:51:32.631 --> 00:51:34.341
It didn't scare me enough then.

00:51:35.551 --> 00:51:37.094
It does now.

00:51:47.938 --> 00:51:49.315
(RADAR BLEEPS)

00:51:49.481 --> 00:51:50.482
What was that?

00:51:50.649 --> 00:51:51.859
Nothing, admiral.

00:51:52.026 --> 00:51:53.402
Passing debris.

00:52:00.701 --> 00:52:02.578
The fleet's only got
18 hours of fuel left.

00:52:02.953 --> 00:52:04.288
We gotta hurry.

00:52:05.581 --> 00:52:07.541
Still can't reach the Resistance?

00:52:07.625 --> 00:52:09.335
- (CHEWIE GROWLS)
- Keep at it.

00:52:09.501 --> 00:52:11.170
If you get through, check their status.

00:52:11.337 --> 00:52:12.630
And ask about Finn.

00:52:12.713 --> 00:52:14.715
(CHEWIE GROWLING)

00:52:15.633 --> 00:52:17.509
(PORG CHEEPING)

00:52:17.760 --> 00:52:18.761
(CHEWIE GROANING)

00:52:19.595 --> 00:52:20.846
(PORG CHIRPING)

00:52:22.723 --> 00:52:24.767
(THUNDER RUMBLING)

00:52:47.831 --> 00:52:49.792
Why is the Force connecting us?

00:52:50.167 --> 00:52:51.168
You and I.

00:52:51.335 --> 00:52:52.711
Murderous snake.

00:52:53.462 --> 00:52:56.507
You're too late.
You lost. I found Skywalker.

00:52:57.800 --> 00:52:59.009
Did he tell you what happened?

00:53:00.386 --> 00:53:02.554
The night I destroyed his temple,
did he tell you why?

00:53:02.721 --> 00:53:05.307
I know everything
I need to know about you.

00:53:05.474 --> 00:53:07.017
You do?

00:53:09.561 --> 00:53:11.480
Ah, you do.

00:53:12.773 --> 00:53:14.692
You have that look in your eyes.

00:53:14.858 --> 00:53:16.652
From the forest.

00:53:19.321 --> 00:53:20.572
When you called me a monster.

00:53:20.739 --> 00:53:22.825
You are a monster.

00:53:28.080 --> 00:53:29.456
Yes, I am.

00:53:53.772 --> 00:53:54.773
ROSE: Okay.

00:53:54.940 --> 00:53:57.192
We get in, we find this codebreaker,
we get out.

00:53:57.359 --> 00:53:59.570
You know this town? Canto Bight?

00:53:59.737 --> 00:54:00.904
From stories.

00:54:01.071 --> 00:54:04.533
It's a terrible place filled with
the worst people in the galaxy.

00:54:04.658 --> 00:54:05.659
Great.

00:54:07.286 --> 00:54:09.329
(SPEAKING ALIEN DIALECT)

00:54:13.792 --> 00:54:15.836
(PASSENGERS MURMURING EXCITEDLY)

00:54:26.889 --> 00:54:28.515
SLOWEN LO: I told those two, I said,

00:54:28.682 --> 00:54:31.351
"This is a public beach.
You can't park that shuttle here."

00:54:31.518 --> 00:54:34.104
But they just lit off toward the casino.

00:54:40.110 --> 00:54:41.111
(UPBEAT MUSIC PLAYING)

00:54:41.236 --> 00:54:42.696
Place your bets. Place your bets.

00:54:42.863 --> 00:54:44.656
All bets on the table
right now, right now!

00:54:44.740 --> 00:54:45.783
Place your bets here.

00:54:46.200 --> 00:54:47.701
(INDISTINCT CHATTER)

00:54:57.586 --> 00:54:58.587
(EXHALES)

00:54:59.421 --> 00:55:02.549
FINN: Aw, yes!
This place is great!

00:55:03.217 --> 00:55:04.510
Okay.

00:55:06.845 --> 00:55:10.390
Maz said this Master Codebreaker
would have a red plom bloom on his lapel.

00:55:10.557 --> 00:55:12.309
Let's find him and get out of here.

00:55:12.476 --> 00:55:14.520
Well played. The house wins.

00:55:14.603 --> 00:55:15.729
(LARGE ALIEN ROARING)

00:55:15.813 --> 00:55:16.814
CROUPIER: Where are
your manners, more like?

00:55:16.897 --> 00:55:17.940
ROSE: Come on!

00:55:22.444 --> 00:55:23.445
(BB-8 CHIRPS)

00:55:23.529 --> 00:55:24.530
(SPEAKING ALIEN DIALECT)

00:55:25.322 --> 00:55:27.366
(BB-8 CHIRPING NERVOUSLY)

00:55:27.866 --> 00:55:28.867
(GRUNTS)

00:55:29.159 --> 00:55:30.160
(BB-8 MOANS SOFTLY)

00:55:30.452 --> 00:55:31.453
(SPEAKING ALIEN DIALECT)

00:55:31.662 --> 00:55:32.663
(BB-8 CHIRPS)

00:55:32.746 --> 00:55:33.747
(BELCHING)

00:55:33.831 --> 00:55:35.874
(BB-8 CHIRPING)

00:55:36.625 --> 00:55:37.626
(ALIEN GROANS)

00:55:41.713 --> 00:55:42.714
FINN: We've covered this whole casino.

00:55:42.798 --> 00:55:43.799
Zero red plom blooms.

00:55:43.882 --> 00:55:45.133
- Where is this guy?
- (DISHES CLATTERING)

00:55:50.264 --> 00:55:51.974
Were those what I think they were?

00:55:52.516 --> 00:55:54.059
(ANNOUNCER SPEAKING ALIEN DIALECT)

00:55:54.142 --> 00:55:55.519
(CROWD CHEERING)

00:55:59.147 --> 00:56:01.149
FINN: What are those things?
ROSE: Fathiers.

00:56:02.067 --> 00:56:03.610
I've never seen a real one.

00:56:04.278 --> 00:56:06.905
Look, this whole place is beautiful.
I mean, come on.

00:56:07.698 --> 00:56:09.324
Why do you hate it so much?

00:56:10.284 --> 00:56:11.577
Look closer.

00:56:16.748 --> 00:56:19.585
ROSE: My sister and I grew up
in a poor mining system.

00:56:20.002 --> 00:56:21.169
(ZAPPING)

00:56:21.253 --> 00:56:24.506
ROSE: The First Order stripped our ore
to finance their military

00:56:25.924 --> 00:56:28.051
then shelled us
to test their weapons.

00:56:28.427 --> 00:56:30.220
(SHOUTING IN ALIEN DIALECT)

00:56:34.099 --> 00:56:36.143
They took everything we had.

00:56:37.477 --> 00:56:40.022
And who do you think
these people are?

00:56:40.522 --> 00:56:43.942
There's only one business in the galaxy
that'll get you this rich.

00:56:44.651 --> 00:56:45.777
War.

00:56:46.236 --> 00:56:48.614
Selling weapons to the First Order.

00:56:50.616 --> 00:56:55.370
I wish I could put my fist through this
whole lousy, beautiful town.

00:56:57.247 --> 00:56:59.291
(BB-8 CHIRPING EXCITEDLY)

00:57:02.794 --> 00:57:03.837
Red plom bloom!

00:57:04.254 --> 00:57:05.255
(GUESTS GASP)

00:57:12.095 --> 00:57:13.138
Red plom bloom!

00:57:13.305 --> 00:57:14.473
The Master Codebreaker!

00:57:20.854 --> 00:57:22.397
Yep, those are the shuttle parkers.

00:57:22.481 --> 00:57:23.523
(ZAPPING)

00:57:23.607 --> 00:57:24.608
OFFICER: All right.

00:57:24.733 --> 00:57:29.154
You two are under arrest
for parking violation 27B/6.

00:57:29.321 --> 00:57:30.322
You have the right to remain...

00:57:30.405 --> 00:57:32.532
- What was that?
- No, no, no. Not now, Lovey.

00:57:32.616 --> 00:57:33.659
I'm on a roll.

00:57:34.660 --> 00:57:35.994
(ALL CHEERING)

00:57:37.913 --> 00:57:39.331
(BB-8 CHIRPS ANXIOUSLY)

00:57:39.831 --> 00:57:40.832
(GRUNTS)

00:57:41.583 --> 00:57:43.126
(PANTING)

00:58:26.920 --> 00:58:27.921
(LIGHTSABER BUZZING)

00:59:17.679 --> 00:59:19.056
LUKE: Lesson two.

00:59:19.222 --> 00:59:23.393
Now that they're extinct,
the Jedi are romanticized, deified.

00:59:23.894 --> 00:59:26.646
But if you strip away the myth
and look at their deeds,

00:59:27.105 --> 00:59:29.149
the legacy of the Jedi is failure.

00:59:29.483 --> 00:59:30.650
Hypocrisy, hubris.

00:59:30.776 --> 00:59:31.777
That's not true.

00:59:31.943 --> 00:59:34.488
At the height of their powers,
they allowed Darth Sidious to rise

00:59:34.654 --> 00:59:36.531
create the Empire, and wipe them out.

00:59:36.907 --> 00:59:38.825
It was a Jedi Master
who was responsible

00:59:38.992 --> 00:59:42.120
for the training
and creation of Darth Vader.

00:59:42.287 --> 00:59:43.789
And a Jedi who saved him.

00:59:44.498 --> 00:59:46.041
Yes, the most hated man in the galaxy.

00:59:46.208 --> 00:59:48.418
But you saw there was conflict inside him.

00:59:48.585 --> 00:59:51.213
You believed that he wasn't gone.
That he could be turned.

00:59:51.546 --> 00:59:53.256
And I became a legend.

00:59:54.591 --> 00:59:56.760
For many years, there was balance

00:59:56.927 --> 00:59:58.303
and then I saw

00:59:58.595 --> 00:59:59.596
Ben.

01:00:01.056 --> 01:00:04.726
My nephew
with that mighty Skywalker blood.

01:00:04.893 --> 01:00:06.228
And in my hubris,

01:00:06.394 --> 01:00:09.564
I thought I could train him,
I could pass on my strengths.

01:00:10.774 --> 01:00:14.069
Han was Han about it, but...

01:00:16.655 --> 01:00:18.156
Leia

01:00:19.616 --> 01:00:21.952
trusted me with her son.

01:00:22.744 --> 01:00:23.745
I took him,

01:00:24.788 --> 01:00:26.540
and a dozen students,

01:00:27.582 --> 01:00:29.126
and began a training temple.

01:00:31.294 --> 01:00:33.296
By the time I realized

01:00:33.380 --> 01:00:36.591
I was no match for
the darkness rising in him,

01:00:37.217 --> 01:00:38.760
it was too late.

01:00:40.095 --> 01:00:41.429
What happened?

01:00:44.891 --> 01:00:46.351
LUKE: I went to confront him.

01:00:48.645 --> 01:00:50.313
And he turned on me.

01:00:50.730 --> 01:00:52.190
Ben, no!

01:00:55.318 --> 01:00:57.445
LUKE: He must have thought
I was dead.

01:00:59.114 --> 01:01:00.365
When I came to,

01:01:02.450 --> 01:01:04.119
the temple was burning.

01:01:05.579 --> 01:01:08.248
He had vanished
with a handful of my students.

01:01:09.332 --> 01:01:11.501
And slaughtered the rest.

01:01:12.961 --> 01:01:14.963
Leia blamed Snoke,

01:01:15.630 --> 01:01:16.882
but it was me.

01:01:17.591 --> 01:01:19.009
I failed.

01:01:22.512 --> 01:01:25.557
Because I was Luke Skywalker.

01:01:26.474 --> 01:01:28.393
Jedi Master.

01:01:33.732 --> 01:01:35.400
A legend.

01:01:37.611 --> 01:01:39.863
The galaxy may need a legend.

01:01:44.492 --> 01:01:48.747
I need someone to show me
my place in all this.

01:01:54.586 --> 01:01:56.338
And you didn't fail Kylo.

01:01:56.504 --> 01:01:58.173
Kylo failed you.

01:01:58.882 --> 01:02:00.550
I won't.

01:02:21.238 --> 01:02:24.074
The main cruiser's
still keeping beyond range.

01:02:24.574 --> 01:02:26.409
But their medical frigate is out of fuel

01:02:27.535 --> 01:02:29.287
and its shields are down.

01:02:29.454 --> 01:02:31.331
The beginning of their end.

01:02:32.791 --> 01:02:34.542
Destroy it.

01:02:37.587 --> 01:02:40.924
The last of our crew has been evacuated
and heading your way.

01:02:41.967 --> 01:02:43.593
It's been an honor, admiral.

01:02:43.760 --> 01:02:45.637
Godspeed, Rebels!

01:02:49.015 --> 01:02:50.058
CONNIX: Admiral,

01:02:50.767 --> 01:02:52.727
fuel reserves at six hours.

01:02:54.521 --> 01:02:56.564
Maintain our current course.

01:02:57.399 --> 01:02:59.067
Steady on.

01:03:04.155 --> 01:03:05.156
Finn,

01:03:05.323 --> 01:03:07.450
Rose, where are you guys?

01:03:12.789 --> 01:03:13.957
Deal me in.

01:03:17.085 --> 01:03:18.086
Thanks.

01:03:18.169 --> 01:03:19.462
(BB-8 MOANING SOFTLY)

01:03:20.046 --> 01:03:23.258
ROSE: Finn, the fleet
is running on fumes.

01:03:24.134 --> 01:03:26.886
Without a codebreaker
to break us onto Snoke's Star Destroyer...

01:03:26.970 --> 01:03:28.013
- (CLANGING)
- (FINN GRUNTS)

01:03:28.096 --> 01:03:29.681
- What do we do?
- FINN: I don't know.

01:03:30.223 --> 01:03:32.851
Unless you got a thief in your pocket,
our plan is shot.

01:03:34.936 --> 01:03:36.229
DJ: Um, I can do it.

01:03:40.400 --> 01:03:41.401
What?

01:03:43.069 --> 01:03:44.195
What?

01:03:45.155 --> 01:03:46.156
What?

01:03:46.323 --> 01:03:47.907
DJ: S-S-Sorry, I just

01:03:48.325 --> 01:03:50.368
couldn't help but overhear all the stuff

01:03:50.452 --> 01:03:53.413
that you were saying really loudly

01:03:54.080 --> 01:03:55.457
while I was trying to sleep.

01:03:57.625 --> 01:03:59.044
Codebreaker?

01:04:00.003 --> 01:04:01.421
Thief?

01:04:02.380 --> 01:04:03.590
I can do it.

01:04:03.757 --> 01:04:06.509
We're not talking about
picking pockets, okay?

01:04:07.552 --> 01:04:09.471
Yeah.

01:04:11.431 --> 01:04:13.391
D-D-Don't let the wrapper
fool you, friend.

01:04:14.100 --> 01:04:17.645
Me and the First Order
codeage go way back.

01:04:19.564 --> 01:04:20.607
And,

01:04:22.317 --> 01:04:24.194
if the price is right,

01:04:25.528 --> 01:04:30.367
I could break you into
old man S-S-Snoke's boudoir.

01:04:32.160 --> 01:04:34.037
- No.
- We're... We got it covered.

01:04:37.665 --> 01:04:38.958
Ha-tuk-ga.

01:04:52.430 --> 01:04:54.182
- Did he just...
- Yeah.

01:04:55.767 --> 01:04:57.394
We gotta get out of here!
This way!

01:04:57.560 --> 01:04:58.645
GUARD: Why you little...

01:04:58.728 --> 01:04:59.729
(BB-8 CHIRPING)

01:05:00.188 --> 01:05:02.232
(GUARDS MUMBLING)

01:05:03.775 --> 01:05:05.568
D-D-Did you do this?

01:05:05.652 --> 01:05:07.278
(BB-8 CHIRPING)

01:05:08.696 --> 01:05:09.739
Hey, hands up!

01:05:10.865 --> 01:05:13.118
- Hands up!
- Yeah, man.

01:05:14.702 --> 01:05:15.703
(GROANING)

01:05:19.541 --> 01:05:20.542
(GRUNTS)

01:05:23.086 --> 01:05:24.087
(BLOWS)

01:05:27.173 --> 01:05:28.383
(BB-8 CHIRPING INQUISITIVELY)

01:05:29.259 --> 01:05:30.844
What's your story, roundie?

01:05:31.553 --> 01:05:32.637
They went this way!

01:05:32.720 --> 01:05:34.722
(INDISTINCT SHOUTING)

01:05:37.392 --> 01:05:39.394
- Lock down all the exits.
- Wait.

01:05:43.940 --> 01:05:45.567
That smelled great.

01:05:45.733 --> 01:05:47.569
Those cops will be here
any minute. What now?

01:05:48.820 --> 01:05:50.363
- (FATHIER GROANING)
- (FINN SHRIEKING)

01:05:53.199 --> 01:05:54.909
Whoa! Ooh!

01:05:55.660 --> 01:05:56.661
(LAUGHS)

01:05:58.121 --> 01:05:59.998
(FATHIER MOANS)

01:06:20.894 --> 01:06:22.604
No, wait. Please, don't!

01:06:29.986 --> 01:06:31.237
ROSE: We're with the Resistance.

01:06:37.243 --> 01:06:39.204
OFFICER 1: Roger that.
Checking the stables now.

01:06:39.787 --> 01:06:40.997
(FATHIER GRUNTING)

01:06:46.127 --> 01:06:47.128
OFFICER 2: This way.

01:06:47.212 --> 01:06:48.213
OFFICER 3: They must have
come through here.

01:06:48.296 --> 01:06:49.714
(DOORS OPENING)

01:06:51.174 --> 01:06:52.425
(FATHIER BRAYS)

01:06:54.344 --> 01:06:55.345
ROSE: Hyah!

01:06:57.222 --> 01:06:58.765
(OFFICERS GROANING)

01:07:01.226 --> 01:07:03.228
Go, go, go! Whoo!

01:07:07.065 --> 01:07:08.149
(FATHIERS BLEATING)

01:07:08.233 --> 01:07:09.275
(ROSE WHOOPING)

01:07:09.359 --> 01:07:10.693
FINN: Stop enjoying this!
Stop enjoying this!

01:07:10.777 --> 01:07:11.778
(ROSE LAUGHS)

01:07:17.367 --> 01:07:19.577
SPEEDER PILOT: We've got them.
They're not going anywhere.

01:07:20.119 --> 01:07:21.246
(FATHIER BRAYING)

01:07:24.123 --> 01:07:25.583
(BOTH GRUNTING)

01:07:25.667 --> 01:07:26.668
BOTH: Ahhh!

01:07:27.377 --> 01:07:29.420
(CROWD SCREAMING)

01:07:35.468 --> 01:07:36.678
(VOCALIZING)

01:07:36.761 --> 01:07:37.762
Huh?

01:07:38.638 --> 01:07:39.847
(ALIEN YELLING)

01:07:39.931 --> 01:07:40.932
(ROSE SCREAMING)

01:07:42.475 --> 01:07:43.893
(LAUGHING)

01:07:48.565 --> 01:07:50.775
- (FATHIERS STAMPEDING)
- (PANICKED YELLING)

01:07:55.071 --> 01:07:56.322
(DINERS SCREAMING)

01:08:02.704 --> 01:08:03.746
(MAN YELPING)

01:08:03.830 --> 01:08:05.456
ROSE: Move, move, move!
Get out of the way!

01:08:07.292 --> 01:08:09.502
Our ship's on the beach straight ahead!

01:08:11.504 --> 01:08:12.505
We need cover!

01:08:14.257 --> 01:08:15.967
(BOTH SCREAMING)

01:08:20.346 --> 01:08:22.390
(BOTH GRUNTING)

01:08:23.391 --> 01:08:24.684
Too much cover!

01:08:37.196 --> 01:08:38.323
There it is!

01:08:40.992 --> 01:08:42.827
BOTH: No!
FINN: Come on!

01:08:46.539 --> 01:08:47.957
(ROSE SCREAMING)

01:08:50.752 --> 01:08:51.753
(FINN GRUNTS)

01:08:58.092 --> 01:08:59.886
SPEEDER PILOT: Let the herd go.
Stick with the perps.

01:09:05.642 --> 01:09:06.684
Where'd they go?

01:09:09.937 --> 01:09:10.980
I think we lost him!

01:09:11.147 --> 01:09:12.815
Now we get down to the beach
and circle back around...

01:09:12.982 --> 01:09:13.983
Cliff!

01:09:14.901 --> 01:09:15.902
(ROSE SCREAMS)

01:09:20.907 --> 01:09:22.784
(BOTH PANTING)

01:09:24.160 --> 01:09:25.203
ROSE: We're trapped.

01:09:25.286 --> 01:09:26.663
(SPEEDERS APPROACHING)

01:09:28.164 --> 01:09:29.374
It was worth it, though.

01:09:29.999 --> 01:09:31.292
To tear up that town,

01:09:31.626 --> 01:09:32.877
make 'em hurt.

01:09:34.504 --> 01:09:35.672
(FATHIER GRUNTS)

01:09:42.470 --> 01:09:43.471
ROSE: Go.

01:09:48.518 --> 01:09:49.769
Now it's worth it.

01:10:00.029 --> 01:10:01.030
SPEEDER PILOT: There they are.

01:10:05.284 --> 01:10:06.577
(BB-8 CHIRPING)

01:10:06.661 --> 01:10:09.205
BB-8! Wait, are you flying that thing?

01:10:09.288 --> 01:10:10.957
(BB-8 CHIRPING EXCITEDLY)

01:10:12.959 --> 01:10:14.252
DJ: Ah.

01:10:15.253 --> 01:10:16.921
N-N-Need a lift?

01:10:45.366 --> 01:10:46.367
(WIND WHISTLING)

01:11:03.676 --> 01:11:04.969
(MACHINES BEEPING)

01:11:10.808 --> 01:11:11.809
Luke.

01:11:13.102 --> 01:11:14.270
Leia.

01:11:23.112 --> 01:11:24.989
I'd rather not do this now.

01:11:25.698 --> 01:11:27.033
KYLO REN: Yeah, me, too.

01:11:29.410 --> 01:11:30.995
Why did you hate your father?

01:11:35.458 --> 01:11:36.459
Do you have something,

01:11:36.542 --> 01:11:37.919
a cowl or something you could put on?

01:11:40.588 --> 01:11:41.631
(SIGHS)

01:11:41.714 --> 01:11:44.008
Why did you hate your father?
Give me an honest answer.

01:11:45.593 --> 01:11:48.137
You had a father who loved you,
he gave a damn about you.

01:11:48.304 --> 01:11:50.348
- I didn't hate him.
- Then why?

01:11:50.765 --> 01:11:51.766
Why what?

01:11:55.269 --> 01:11:56.729
Why what? Say it.

01:11:58.022 --> 01:11:59.357
Why did you...

01:12:00.149 --> 01:12:02.109
Why did you kill him? (SOBS)

01:12:02.568 --> 01:12:03.778
I don't understand.

01:12:03.903 --> 01:12:04.904
KYLO REN: No?

01:12:05.071 --> 01:12:06.697
Your parents threw you away
like garbage.

01:12:06.864 --> 01:12:08.950
- They didn't!
- They did.

01:12:09.116 --> 01:12:10.910
But you can't stop needing them.

01:12:11.077 --> 01:12:12.328
It's your greatest weakness.

01:12:13.162 --> 01:12:14.247
Looking for them everywhere,

01:12:14.413 --> 01:12:15.581
in Han Solo,

01:12:16.082 --> 01:12:17.875
now in Skywalker.

01:12:21.295 --> 01:12:23.089
Did he tell you what happened
that night?

01:12:23.422 --> 01:12:24.423
Yes.

01:12:26.509 --> 01:12:27.593
No.

01:12:29.345 --> 01:12:31.013
KYLO REN: He had sensed my power,

01:12:32.306 --> 01:12:34.058
as he senses yours.

01:12:35.309 --> 01:12:37.019
And he feared it.

01:12:44.402 --> 01:12:45.736
(LIGHTSABER ACTIVATING)

01:12:53.828 --> 01:12:55.121
Liar.

01:12:59.542 --> 01:13:00.918
Let the past die.

01:13:02.503 --> 01:13:04.839
Kill it if you have to.

01:13:07.383 --> 01:13:10.136
That's the only way to become
what you were meant to be.

01:13:53.304 --> 01:13:55.222
No! No!

01:14:35.721 --> 01:14:37.139
FEMALE VOICE: Rey?

01:14:54.198 --> 01:14:56.242
(FINGERS SNAPPING)

01:15:06.210 --> 01:15:08.879
REY: I should have felt
trapped or panicked.

01:15:09.046 --> 01:15:10.506
But I didn't.

01:15:13.926 --> 01:15:14.927
This didn't go on forever,

01:15:15.011 --> 01:15:17.179
I knew it was leading somewhere.

01:15:17.930 --> 01:15:20.391
And that, at the end,
it would show me what I came to see.

01:15:22.560 --> 01:15:23.978
FEMALE VOICE: Rey.

01:15:32.486 --> 01:15:34.697
Let me see them.

01:15:35.156 --> 01:15:37.158
My parents,

01:15:37.324 --> 01:15:39.410
please.

01:15:42.788 --> 01:15:44.832
(BREATHING HEAVILY)

01:16:14.528 --> 01:16:16.614
REY: I thought I'd find answers here.

01:16:18.199 --> 01:16:19.575
I was wrong.

01:16:22.119 --> 01:16:23.871
I'd never felt so alone.

01:16:26.415 --> 01:16:27.792
You're not alone.

01:16:32.922 --> 01:16:34.256
Neither are you.

01:16:35.299 --> 01:16:36.592
Rey?

01:16:44.391 --> 01:16:46.060
It isn't too late.

01:17:10.042 --> 01:17:11.585
(BREATHING SHAKILY)

01:17:43.784 --> 01:17:44.827
Stop!

01:17:54.211 --> 01:17:57.131
Is it true?
Did you try to murder him?

01:17:57.298 --> 01:17:59.717
Leave this island now!

01:17:59.884 --> 01:18:01.093
Stop.

01:18:02.344 --> 01:18:03.345
Stop!

01:18:04.471 --> 01:18:05.764
(GRUNTING)

01:18:07.933 --> 01:18:09.018
Did you do it?

01:18:09.185 --> 01:18:11.187
Did you create Kylo Ren?

01:18:12.229 --> 01:18:13.272
(GRUNTS)

01:18:14.857 --> 01:18:15.858
(PANTING)

01:18:19.695 --> 01:18:20.696
(REY SHRIEKS)

01:18:21.405 --> 01:18:23.157
(REY GRUNTING)

01:18:40.883 --> 01:18:42.426
- Tell me the truth.
- (LIGHTSABER DEACTIVATING)

01:18:48.682 --> 01:18:50.643
I saw darkness.

01:18:52.436 --> 01:18:54.355
I'd sensed it building in him.

01:18:54.521 --> 01:18:57.149
I'd seen it in moments
during his training.

01:18:57.691 --> 01:18:59.526
But then I looked inside,

01:18:59.944 --> 01:19:02.738
and it was beyond
what I ever imagined.

01:19:02.947 --> 01:19:04.323
(LIGHTSABERS CLASHING)

01:19:04.406 --> 01:19:06.116
(DISTANT SCREAMING)

01:19:07.952 --> 01:19:10.120
Snoke had already turned his heart.

01:19:11.789 --> 01:19:14.541
He would bring destruction,
and pain, and death,

01:19:14.625 --> 01:19:17.670
and the end of everything I love
because of what he will become.

01:19:17.753 --> 01:19:19.630
And for the briefest moment
of pure instinct,

01:19:19.713 --> 01:19:22.007
- I thought I could stop it.
- (LIGHTSABER ACTIVATING)

01:19:24.093 --> 01:19:26.553
It passed like a fleeting shadow.

01:19:27.429 --> 01:19:29.306
And I was left with shame,

01:19:30.641 --> 01:19:32.601
and with consequence.

01:19:33.352 --> 01:19:35.229
And the last thing I saw

01:19:35.771 --> 01:19:37.690
were the eyes of a frightened boy

01:19:37.773 --> 01:19:40.234
whose master had failed him.

01:19:41.902 --> 01:19:42.903
Ben, no!

01:19:49.827 --> 01:19:51.954
You failed him by thinking
his choice was made.

01:19:52.037 --> 01:19:53.038
It wasn't.

01:19:53.497 --> 01:19:55.291
There's still conflict in him.

01:19:55.457 --> 01:19:58.085
If he were turned from the dark side,
that could shift the tide.

01:19:58.252 --> 01:20:00.004
This could be how we win.

01:20:00.170 --> 01:20:03.173
This is not going to go
the way you think.

01:20:03.674 --> 01:20:04.925
It is.

01:20:05.134 --> 01:20:07.886
Just now when we touched hands,

01:20:08.053 --> 01:20:09.305
I saw his future.

01:20:10.306 --> 01:20:11.974
As solid as I'm seeing you.

01:20:12.433 --> 01:20:15.978
If I go to him, Ben Solo will turn.

01:20:16.145 --> 01:20:17.271
Rey,

01:20:17.771 --> 01:20:19.857
don't do this.

01:20:35.706 --> 01:20:37.333
Then he's our last hope.

01:21:18.415 --> 01:21:19.833
Master Yoda.

01:21:20.667 --> 01:21:23.128
Young Skywalker.

01:21:25.381 --> 01:21:26.840
I'm ending all of this.

01:21:27.174 --> 01:21:29.635
The tree, the text, the Jedi.

01:21:29.802 --> 01:21:31.011
I'm gonna burn it down.

01:21:50.823 --> 01:21:51.990
Hmm.

01:22:03.001 --> 01:22:04.628
(LAUGHING)

01:22:08.382 --> 01:22:09.842
Ah, Skywalker.

01:22:09.925 --> 01:22:10.968
Missed you, have I.

01:22:15.639 --> 01:22:16.640
(GRUNTS)

01:22:24.148 --> 01:22:25.816
So it is time

01:22:27.359 --> 01:22:29.153
for the Jedi Order to end.

01:22:29.319 --> 01:22:31.572
Time it is.

01:22:32.156 --> 01:22:33.657
Hmm.

01:22:36.285 --> 01:22:41.874
For you to look past
a pile of old books, hmm?

01:22:41.957 --> 01:22:43.709
The sacred Jedi texts.

01:22:43.876 --> 01:22:46.044
Oh. Read them, have you?

01:22:46.753 --> 01:22:48.213
- Well, I...
- Page-turners

01:22:48.380 --> 01:22:49.631
they were not.

01:22:50.299 --> 01:22:52.176
Yes, yes, yes.

01:22:52.342 --> 01:22:53.677
Wisdom they held,

01:22:53.844 --> 01:22:57.306
but that library contained
nothing that the girl Rey

01:22:57.473 --> 01:22:59.391
does not already possess.

01:23:02.561 --> 01:23:04.229
Skywalker,

01:23:05.147 --> 01:23:07.065
still looking to the horizon.

01:23:07.232 --> 01:23:09.735
Never here, now, hmm?

01:23:09.902 --> 01:23:12.488
The need in front of your nose.

01:23:13.280 --> 01:23:14.281
Hmm?

01:23:16.158 --> 01:23:17.784
I was weak.

01:23:19.036 --> 01:23:20.037
Unwise.

01:23:20.204 --> 01:23:22.748
Lost Ben Solo, you did.

01:23:23.499 --> 01:23:25.918
Lose Rey, we must not.

01:23:26.376 --> 01:23:29.171
I can't be what she needs me to be.

01:23:29.796 --> 01:23:32.007
Heeded my words not, did you?

01:23:32.424 --> 01:23:34.968
Pass on what you have learned.

01:23:35.135 --> 01:23:37.221
Strength, mastery.

01:23:38.180 --> 01:23:39.806
But weakness,

01:23:39.973 --> 01:23:42.351
folly, failure also.

01:23:42.518 --> 01:23:45.646
Yes, failure most of all.

01:23:45.812 --> 01:23:48.774
The greatest teacher, failure is.

01:23:51.902 --> 01:23:53.946
(YODA GRUNTING)

01:23:58.075 --> 01:23:59.076
Luke,

01:24:01.662 --> 01:24:05.082
we are what they grow beyond.

01:24:05.832 --> 01:24:10.045
That is the true burden of all masters.

01:24:23.267 --> 01:24:25.227
Four parsecs to go.
This thing really cooks.

01:24:25.394 --> 01:24:27.062
I just hope we're in time.

01:24:27.229 --> 01:24:28.647
You can actually do this, right?

01:24:29.189 --> 01:24:31.191
Yeah, about that...

01:24:34.945 --> 01:24:38.407
Guys, I can do it.

01:24:39.324 --> 01:24:42.035
But there exists a pre-"do it"
conversation about price.

01:24:42.786 --> 01:24:45.163
Once we're done, the Resistance
will give you whatever you want.

01:24:46.039 --> 01:24:47.082
What you got deposit-wise?

01:24:47.958 --> 01:24:50.168
Are you kidding me?
Look at us.

01:24:51.253 --> 01:24:53.005
Is that Haysian smelt?

01:24:55.632 --> 01:24:56.967
That's something.

01:24:57.134 --> 01:24:59.303
No, we gave you our word.
You're gonna get paid.

01:24:59.428 --> 01:25:00.637
That should be enough.

01:25:00.804 --> 01:25:02.097
DJ: Guys, I wanna keep helping.

01:25:03.181 --> 01:25:06.685
But no something, n-n-no doing.

01:25:06.852 --> 01:25:08.854
Okay, listen here, you've got...

01:25:09.396 --> 01:25:11.023
Do it.

01:25:14.067 --> 01:25:15.861
Now I can help.

01:25:18.363 --> 01:25:19.448
Give it back.

01:25:20.907 --> 01:25:21.908
DJ: What?

01:25:21.992 --> 01:25:24.077
FINN: Give it back!

01:25:24.244 --> 01:25:26.121
You have no idea how much
that medallion means to her.

01:25:26.663 --> 01:25:29.708
What are you... Why are you
ransacking your own ship?

01:25:30.584 --> 01:25:31.585
(SIGHS)

01:25:32.169 --> 01:25:33.253
It's not your ship.

01:25:33.337 --> 01:25:34.963
(BB-8 CHIRPING)

01:25:35.047 --> 01:25:36.089
He says I stole it.

01:25:36.256 --> 01:25:38.425
- Yeah, I got that.
- We stole it.

01:25:38.508 --> 01:25:39.885
(BB-8 CHIRPS)

01:25:40.344 --> 01:25:42.596
At least you're stealing
from the bad guys

01:25:43.221 --> 01:25:44.222
and helping the good.

01:25:44.389 --> 01:25:46.350
Good guys, bad guys,

01:25:46.516 --> 01:25:48.560
made-up words.

01:25:49.269 --> 01:25:52.856
Let's see who formerly owned
this gorgeous hunk-uh.

01:25:55.942 --> 01:25:58.153
Ah, this guy was an arms dealer.

01:25:58.945 --> 01:26:02.157
Made his bank selling weapons
to the bad guys.

01:26:03.867 --> 01:26:04.868
Oh...

01:26:06.495 --> 01:26:07.954
And the good.

01:26:09.414 --> 01:26:12.334
Finn, let me learn you something big.

01:26:13.710 --> 01:26:15.837
It's all a machine, partner.

01:26:17.506 --> 01:26:20.342
Live free, don't join.

01:26:32.396 --> 01:26:34.815
That was the last of their support ships.

01:26:34.981 --> 01:26:36.024
It's just their main cruiser now.

01:26:36.608 --> 01:26:38.068
And their fuel reserve?

01:26:38.235 --> 01:26:39.945
By our calculation,

01:26:40.112 --> 01:26:41.613
critical.

01:26:45.826 --> 01:26:46.827
She in there?

01:26:46.910 --> 01:26:47.911
The admiral's banned you
from the bridge.

01:26:48.036 --> 01:26:49.496
- Let's not have a scene.
- No, let's.

01:26:49.621 --> 01:26:51.498
POE: Holdo?
D'ACY: You're not allowed in here.

01:26:51.581 --> 01:26:54.000
- Flyboy.
- Cut it, lady.

01:26:54.084 --> 01:26:55.794
We had a fleet,
now we're down to one ship,

01:26:55.877 --> 01:26:57.587
and you've told us nothing!

01:26:58.088 --> 01:27:01.299
Tell us that we have a plan!

01:27:01.466 --> 01:27:02.467
That there's hope!

01:27:02.634 --> 01:27:04.052
When I served under Leia,

01:27:04.219 --> 01:27:06.680
she would say,
hope is like the sun.

01:27:06.847 --> 01:27:09.349
If you only believe in it
when you can see it...

01:27:09.516 --> 01:27:11.768
You'll never make it
through the night.

01:27:12.185 --> 01:27:13.520
Yes.

01:27:14.354 --> 01:27:15.355
(POE SIGHS)

01:27:21.528 --> 01:27:23.655
Are you fueling up the transports?

01:27:29.161 --> 01:27:30.454
You are.

01:27:31.163 --> 01:27:32.414
All of them?

01:27:33.665 --> 01:27:36.293
We're abandoning ship? Is that...

01:27:36.668 --> 01:27:38.545
That's what you got?
That's what you brought us to?

01:27:39.296 --> 01:27:40.297
Coward!

01:27:41.173 --> 01:27:44.050
Those transport ships
are unarmed, unshielded.

01:27:44.217 --> 01:27:46.470
We abandon this cruiser, we're done.

01:27:46.636 --> 01:27:49.347
We don't stand a chance.
No, you are not just a coward,

01:27:49.514 --> 01:27:51.057
you are a traitor.

01:27:51.767 --> 01:27:54.019
Get this man off my bridge.

01:28:00.817 --> 01:28:03.111
POE: (ON RADIO) Finn,
Holdo's loading the crew in the shuttle.

01:28:03.195 --> 01:28:04.988
She's going to abandon ship.
Where are you?

01:28:05.155 --> 01:28:06.865
Poe, we're on our way
back to the fleet.

01:28:07.032 --> 01:28:08.200
We're so close.

01:28:08.366 --> 01:28:09.409
Did you find the Master Codebreaker?

01:28:09.576 --> 01:28:11.661
Well, we found a codebreaker.

01:28:12.120 --> 01:28:13.205
We can shut the tracker down.

01:28:13.288 --> 01:28:15.290
Just buy us a little more time.

01:28:16.374 --> 01:28:18.001
All right. Hurry.

01:28:23.215 --> 01:28:24.966
As soon as I launch,
you jump back out of range.

01:28:25.133 --> 01:28:27.886
Stay there until you get my signal
for where to rendezvous.

01:28:27.969 --> 01:28:29.054
(R2-D2 BEEPS)

01:28:29.679 --> 01:28:32.474
- (CHEWIE GROWLS)
- If you see Finn before I do,

01:28:32.557 --> 01:28:33.558
tell him...

01:28:33.642 --> 01:28:35.227
(CHEWIE GROWLS)

01:28:35.769 --> 01:28:37.521
Yeah, perfect. Tell him that.

01:28:37.604 --> 01:28:38.605
(CHEWIE GRUNTS)

01:29:16.059 --> 01:29:17.853
(BREATHING HEAVILY)

01:29:19.688 --> 01:29:20.689
(GASPS)

01:29:44.504 --> 01:29:46.840
DJ: Cloaking our approach.
We should be off their scopes.

01:29:47.632 --> 01:29:49.968
Then we slice a slit in their shield.

01:29:50.135 --> 01:29:51.761
Blip bloppity bloop,

01:29:52.804 --> 01:29:54.764
and slip right through.

01:29:58.518 --> 01:30:01.062
(BUZZING)

01:30:03.773 --> 01:30:05.066
(BUZZING STOPS)

01:30:13.199 --> 01:30:16.328
So a stormtrooper
and a who now are doing what?

01:30:16.494 --> 01:30:17.621
They are trying to save us.

01:30:17.787 --> 01:30:19.414
This is our best chance for escape.

01:30:19.581 --> 01:30:21.499
You have to give Finn and Rose
all the time that you can.

01:30:21.666 --> 01:30:24.044
You have bet the survival
of the Resistance

01:30:24.210 --> 01:30:26.963
on bad odds and put us all at risk.

01:30:27.130 --> 01:30:28.298
There's no time now.

01:30:28.465 --> 01:30:30.467
We have to get clear of the cruiser.
Load the transports.

01:30:30.550 --> 01:30:31.551
CREW MEMBER: Right away, admiral.

01:30:31.635 --> 01:30:32.761
Yeah, I was afraid you'd say that.

01:30:32.844 --> 01:30:34.804
- (GUNS COCKING)
- Vice Admiral Holdo,

01:30:34.888 --> 01:30:36.681
I am relieving you
of your command

01:30:36.848 --> 01:30:40.101
for the survival of this ship,
its crew, and the Resistance.

01:30:41.019 --> 01:30:43.229
I hope you understand
what you're doing.

01:30:43.772 --> 01:30:44.773
Yeah.

01:30:44.981 --> 01:30:46.107
- I'm going to the bridge.
- (C'AI GRUNTS)

01:30:46.274 --> 01:30:48.276
If they move, stun them.

01:31:05.919 --> 01:31:07.212
(BB-8 CHIRPS)

01:31:08.213 --> 01:31:09.965
OFFICER 1:
...at least three cycles so far.

01:31:10.131 --> 01:31:11.633
OFFICER 2: Yes, sir. We are working on it.

01:31:12.467 --> 01:31:13.843
(BB-8 IMITATING MOUSE DROID)

01:31:15.470 --> 01:31:16.638
(BB-8 WHIRRING CONFUSEDLY)

01:31:18.848 --> 01:31:20.767
OFFICER 3: I will do my best, sir.

01:31:22.811 --> 01:31:23.812
(BB-9E CHIRPING INQUISITIVELY)

01:31:30.944 --> 01:31:32.153
Almost there.

01:31:41.329 --> 01:31:43.081
You don't have to do this.

01:31:43.623 --> 01:31:45.250
I feel the conflict in you.

01:31:45.417 --> 01:31:47.127
It's tearing you apart.

01:31:48.169 --> 01:31:50.505
Ben, when we touched hands,

01:31:50.672 --> 01:31:52.215
I saw your future.

01:31:52.382 --> 01:31:54.801
Just the shape of it,
but solid and clear.

01:31:55.343 --> 01:31:57.595
You will not bow before Snoke.

01:32:00.640 --> 01:32:02.183
You'll turn.

01:32:04.436 --> 01:32:06.062
(WHISPERING) I'll help you.

01:32:06.646 --> 01:32:08.148
I saw it.

01:32:08.314 --> 01:32:09.941
I saw something, too.

01:32:11.401 --> 01:32:12.402
Because of what I saw,

01:32:12.569 --> 01:32:14.988
I know when the moment comes,
you'll be the one to turn.

01:32:15.739 --> 01:32:17.532
You'll stand with me.

01:32:18.199 --> 01:32:19.200
Rey,

01:32:20.410 --> 01:32:22.704
I saw who your parents are.

01:32:37.594 --> 01:32:41.931
Well done, my good
and faithful apprentice.

01:32:42.098 --> 01:32:46.269
My faith in you is restored.

01:32:47.395 --> 01:32:49.647
Young Rey.

01:32:51.775 --> 01:32:53.318
Welcome.

01:32:57.113 --> 01:32:58.114
(BB-8 CHIRPS)

01:32:58.698 --> 01:32:59.949
FINN: So this is it.

01:33:00.116 --> 01:33:01.993
The tracker's right behind this door.

01:33:02.994 --> 01:33:04.579
(INDISTINCT PA CHATTER)

01:33:12.879 --> 01:33:13.880
(ZAPS)

01:33:15.215 --> 01:33:17.300
DJ: Haysian smelt.

01:33:17.759 --> 01:33:19.177
Best conductor.

01:33:27.769 --> 01:33:29.270
And you're welcome.

01:33:31.356 --> 01:33:33.108
Good time to figure out
how we get back to the fleet?

01:33:33.274 --> 01:33:34.943
I know where the nearest escape pods are.

01:33:35.026 --> 01:33:36.027
Course you do.

01:33:36.111 --> 01:33:37.904
POE: BB-8, tell me something good.

01:33:37.987 --> 01:33:38.988
(BB-8 CHIRPS)

01:33:39.781 --> 01:33:40.990
Poe, we're almost there.

01:33:41.157 --> 01:33:42.408
Have the cruiser prepped for lightspeed.

01:33:42.534 --> 01:33:44.744
Yeah, I'm on it, pal. You just hurry.

01:33:46.955 --> 01:33:48.873
Clear the bridge, escort the
officers down to the hangar.

01:33:49.040 --> 01:33:50.542
C-3PO: Commander... Captain Dameron,

01:33:50.625 --> 01:33:52.502
Admiral Holdo was looking for you.

01:33:52.669 --> 01:33:53.837
Yeah, we spoke.

01:33:55.296 --> 01:33:57.507
Sir, I am almost afraid to ask.

01:33:57.674 --> 01:33:59.509
Good instinct, Threepio. Go with that.

01:34:01.970 --> 01:34:03.721
(INDISTINCT CHATTER)

01:34:08.226 --> 01:34:09.394
(GUARDS EXCLAIMING)

01:34:09.894 --> 01:34:10.895
(GRUNTS)

01:34:12.272 --> 01:34:13.273
Seal that door!

01:34:16.067 --> 01:34:17.110
We're running out of time.

01:34:17.193 --> 01:34:18.444
FINN: Come on, how's it going?

01:34:18.611 --> 01:34:20.155
Almost there.

01:34:21.197 --> 01:34:23.032
Threepio, where do you think
you're going?

01:34:23.199 --> 01:34:25.201
It would be quite against
my programming

01:34:25.368 --> 01:34:27.078
- to be party to a mutiny.
- Hey!

01:34:27.245 --> 01:34:29.080
It is not correct protocol.

01:34:29.831 --> 01:34:32.375
Oh! Neither is this!

01:34:32.458 --> 01:34:34.419
Finn? We're ready to make the jump!

01:34:34.586 --> 01:34:35.837
Now or never.

01:34:39.382 --> 01:34:40.800
- Now.
- (MACHINE PROCESSING)

01:34:44.053 --> 01:34:45.763
(CRACKLING)

01:34:47.849 --> 01:34:48.850
You're up.

01:35:02.322 --> 01:35:03.865
(BB-9E BLEEPING)

01:35:06.659 --> 01:35:08.828
STORMTROOPER 1: You there, hands up!
STORMTROOPER 2: Watch 'em, watch 'em.

01:35:08.912 --> 01:35:10.955
STORMTROOPER 1: Drop your weapons, now!
STORMTROOPER 2: Hands up, Rebel scum.

01:35:11.039 --> 01:35:12.707
STORMTROOPER 3:
Get down! I said, down!

01:35:13.958 --> 01:35:14.959
(BB-8 CHIRPS SOFTLY)

01:35:16.336 --> 01:35:17.629
(BB-9E WHIRRING)

01:35:22.467 --> 01:35:24.260
FN-2187.

01:35:26.179 --> 01:35:28.514
So good to have you back.

01:35:29.349 --> 01:35:30.475
They didn't make it.

01:35:44.405 --> 01:35:45.531
Leia.

01:35:53.957 --> 01:35:55.541
(ALARM BLARING)

01:35:57.001 --> 01:35:58.378
MALE PA ANNOUNCER:
Please board the transports

01:35:58.461 --> 01:36:00.755
according to your
evacuation designation.

01:36:00.922 --> 01:36:01.923
All transports must be cleared...

01:36:02.006 --> 01:36:03.174
GURNEY OPERATOR: Okay,
help me push him up, guys.

01:36:03.549 --> 01:36:05.051
HOLDO: That one's a troublemaker.

01:36:05.677 --> 01:36:06.928
I like him.

01:36:07.637 --> 01:36:08.680
Me, too.

01:36:09.389 --> 01:36:11.391
Now, time to board your transport.

01:36:12.558 --> 01:36:14.185
For the transports to escape,

01:36:15.186 --> 01:36:18.147
someone needs to stay behind
and pilot the cruiser.

01:36:22.777 --> 01:36:24.320
Too many losses.

01:36:25.989 --> 01:36:28.116
I can't take any more.

01:36:28.491 --> 01:36:29.742
Sure you can.

01:36:31.160 --> 01:36:33.204
You taught me how.

01:36:35.623 --> 01:36:36.916
BOTH: May the Force be...

01:36:37.000 --> 01:36:38.418
(BOTH CHUCKLING)

01:36:38.960 --> 01:36:40.670
You go on. I've said it enough.

01:36:42.422 --> 01:36:45.925
May the Force be with you always.

01:36:52.640 --> 01:36:53.933
FEMALE PILOT: (ON RADIO)
Cloaking device activated.

01:36:54.017 --> 01:36:55.852
We should be off their scopes.

01:36:56.019 --> 01:36:58.396
Let's hope this works.

01:37:10.825 --> 01:37:11.868
(HANDCUFFS BEEPING)

01:37:15.038 --> 01:37:17.332
Come closer, child.

01:37:20.126 --> 01:37:22.628
So much strength.

01:37:23.004 --> 01:37:26.090
Darkness rises,

01:37:26.299 --> 01:37:30.011
and light to meet it.

01:37:30.928 --> 01:37:34.849
I warned my young apprentice
that as he grew stronger,

01:37:35.141 --> 01:37:37.727
his equal in the light would rise.

01:37:40.313 --> 01:37:41.397
Skywalker...

01:37:41.481 --> 01:37:43.316
(CHUCKLING) I assumed.

01:37:44.400 --> 01:37:45.401
Wrongly.

01:37:48.654 --> 01:37:50.448
Closer, I said.

01:37:57.246 --> 01:37:58.998
REY: You underestimate Skywalker,

01:37:59.707 --> 01:38:00.833
and Ben Solo,

01:38:01.501 --> 01:38:02.794
and me.

01:38:03.419 --> 01:38:05.338
It will be your downfall.

01:38:05.421 --> 01:38:06.589
(WHISPERS) Oh...

01:38:06.964 --> 01:38:08.883
Have you seen something?

01:38:09.300 --> 01:38:12.261
A weakness in my apprentice.

01:38:12.428 --> 01:38:14.430
Is that why you came?

01:38:15.973 --> 01:38:17.100
(LAUGHS)

01:38:17.183 --> 01:38:18.893
Young fool.

01:38:19.060 --> 01:38:22.772
It was I who bridged your minds.

01:38:23.189 --> 01:38:26.567
I stoked Ren's conflicted soul.

01:38:26.734 --> 01:38:29.821
I knew he was not strong enough
to hide it from you.

01:38:29.987 --> 01:38:35.243
And you were not wise enough
to resist the bait.

01:38:38.788 --> 01:38:40.123
And now,

01:38:40.665 --> 01:38:45.503
you will give me Skywalker.

01:38:45.586 --> 01:38:46.629
(REY BREATHING HEAVILY)

01:38:46.712 --> 01:38:49.173
Then I will kill you

01:38:49.340 --> 01:38:52.051
with the cruelest stroke.

01:38:52.885 --> 01:38:53.886
No.

01:38:54.512 --> 01:38:55.763
Yes.

01:38:57.140 --> 01:38:58.141
(GRUNTS)

01:38:59.809 --> 01:39:02.478
Give me

01:39:03.813 --> 01:39:05.523
everything.

01:39:06.065 --> 01:39:07.775
REY: No! No!

01:39:08.234 --> 01:39:09.277
No!

01:39:10.236 --> 01:39:12.613
(SCREAMS)

01:39:13.156 --> 01:39:14.157
(GASPS)

01:39:16.367 --> 01:39:17.994
No. No.

01:39:18.161 --> 01:39:19.370
No, no, no!

01:39:24.292 --> 01:39:25.376
LEIA: Poe.

01:39:31.090 --> 01:39:32.091
What is that?

01:39:32.258 --> 01:39:34.051
D'ACY: The mineral planet, Crait.

01:39:34.218 --> 01:39:36.554
An uncharted hideout from
the days of the Rebellion.

01:39:37.096 --> 01:39:38.973
- That's a Rebel base?
- Abandoned,

01:39:39.432 --> 01:39:40.433
but heavily armored

01:39:40.600 --> 01:39:41.601
with enough power

01:39:41.684 --> 01:39:42.894
to get a distress signal to our allies

01:39:43.060 --> 01:39:44.228
scattered in the Outer Rim.

01:39:44.395 --> 01:39:46.189
LEIA: Holdo knew the First Order

01:39:46.355 --> 01:39:47.523
was tracking our big ship.

01:39:47.690 --> 01:39:50.526
They're not monitoring
for little transports.

01:39:51.027 --> 01:39:53.237
So we could slip down
to the surface unnoticed

01:39:53.404 --> 01:39:56.699
and hide till the First Order passes.

01:39:58.826 --> 01:39:59.911
That could work.

01:40:01.579 --> 01:40:03.539
She was more interested

01:40:03.623 --> 01:40:06.000
in protecting the light than she was

01:40:06.542 --> 01:40:09.045
seeming like a hero.

01:40:21.015 --> 01:40:22.266
Godspeed,

01:40:22.558 --> 01:40:24.018
Rebels.

01:40:39.325 --> 01:40:40.326
(ROSE GRUNTS)

01:40:53.714 --> 01:40:55.091
Well done, Phasma.

01:40:56.217 --> 01:40:58.970
Your ship and payment, as we agreed.

01:41:06.852 --> 01:41:08.437
You lying snake.

01:41:10.064 --> 01:41:11.065
(ROSE STRUGGLING)

01:41:13.276 --> 01:41:15.570
We got caught,

01:41:16.237 --> 01:41:18.322
I cut a d-d-deal.

01:41:19.115 --> 01:41:20.157
Wait,

01:41:20.825 --> 01:41:22.159
cut a deal with what?

01:41:22.326 --> 01:41:23.911
Sir, we checked on the
information from the thief.

01:41:24.453 --> 01:41:26.872
We ran a decloaking scan,
and sure enough,

01:41:27.039 --> 01:41:29.375
30 Resistance transports
have just launched from the cruiser.

01:41:30.543 --> 01:41:32.712
He told us the truth.

01:41:33.504 --> 01:41:35.214
Will wonders never cease?

01:41:35.381 --> 01:41:36.382
No.

01:41:36.841 --> 01:41:37.842
Our weapons are ready?

01:41:38.009 --> 01:41:39.343
Ready and aimed, sir.

01:41:40.219 --> 01:41:41.846
Fire at will.

01:41:42.555 --> 01:41:44.098
Wait. No, no. No, you can't!

01:41:44.640 --> 01:41:46.017
No!

01:41:53.649 --> 01:41:54.817
(PANICKED MURMURING)

01:42:00.156 --> 01:42:01.741
PILOT: Admiral, we're taking fire!

01:42:01.907 --> 01:42:03.367
- Do we turn around?
- No, you're too far out.

01:42:03.534 --> 01:42:05.161
Full speed to planetfall.

01:42:05.328 --> 01:42:06.329
Full speed!

01:42:09.206 --> 01:42:10.207
(GROANS)

01:42:12.126 --> 01:42:14.170
(LAUGHING) Well, well,

01:42:14.253 --> 01:42:18.007
I did not expect Skywalker
to be so wise.

01:42:18.591 --> 01:42:21.177
We will give him and the Jedi Order

01:42:21.344 --> 01:42:23.721
the death he desires.

01:42:24.347 --> 01:42:25.598
After the Rebels are gone,

01:42:25.765 --> 01:42:27.224
we will go to his planet

01:42:27.391 --> 01:42:31.228
and obliterate the entire island.

01:42:35.733 --> 01:42:36.734
(REY YELPING)

01:42:38.027 --> 01:42:39.445
SNOKE: Such spunk.

01:42:40.112 --> 01:42:41.238
Look here now.

01:42:42.114 --> 01:42:43.699
(STRUGGLING)

01:42:48.663 --> 01:42:53.709
SNOKE: The entire Resistance
on those transports...

01:42:54.377 --> 01:42:58.089
Soon they will all be gone.

01:42:58.422 --> 01:43:01.550
For you, all is lost.

01:43:05.596 --> 01:43:09.600
Ooh. And still that fiery spit of hope.

01:43:11.227 --> 01:43:14.397
You have the spirit of a true Jedi!

01:43:16.691 --> 01:43:18.067
(GRUNTING)

01:43:22.863 --> 01:43:24.198
And because of that,

01:43:25.324 --> 01:43:26.701
you must die.

01:43:26.867 --> 01:43:27.868
(STRUGGLING)

01:43:29.537 --> 01:43:31.664
My worthy apprentice,

01:43:31.831 --> 01:43:35.584
son of darkness,
heir apparent to Lord Vader.

01:43:35.751 --> 01:43:39.213
Where there was conflict,
I now sense resolve.

01:43:39.380 --> 01:43:42.091
Where there was weakness, strength.

01:43:42.883 --> 01:43:44.468
Complete your training,

01:43:44.802 --> 01:43:49.181
and fulfill your destiny.

01:43:53.853 --> 01:43:55.438
(BREATHING HEAVILY)

01:43:58.441 --> 01:44:00.109
I know what I have to do.

01:44:02.153 --> 01:44:03.279
Ben.

01:44:03.362 --> 01:44:04.864
(SNOKE LAUGHING)

01:44:04.947 --> 01:44:07.158
You think you can turn him?

01:44:07.700 --> 01:44:09.535
Pathetic child.

01:44:11.078 --> 01:44:13.497
I cannot be betrayed,

01:44:13.664 --> 01:44:15.708
I cannot be beaten.

01:44:15.875 --> 01:44:18.252
I see his mind,

01:44:18.419 --> 01:44:21.464
I see his every intent.

01:44:21.547 --> 01:44:22.548
Yes.

01:44:24.091 --> 01:44:29.764
I see him turning
the lightsaber to strike true.

01:44:30.306 --> 01:44:31.390
And now,

01:44:32.183 --> 01:44:34.059
foolish child,

01:44:34.226 --> 01:44:36.187
he ignites it,

01:44:36.854 --> 01:44:40.399
and kills his true enemy!

01:44:40.524 --> 01:44:41.859
(LIGHTSABER ACTIVATING)

01:45:00.586 --> 01:45:02.213
(LIGHTSABER ACTIVATING)

01:45:21.524 --> 01:45:23.234
Come on, give it full thrusters.
Full speed!

01:45:23.400 --> 01:45:24.819
I am, sir.

01:45:27.488 --> 01:45:28.989
You murdering bastard!

01:45:29.657 --> 01:45:31.784
T-T-Take it easy, Big F.

01:45:32.243 --> 01:45:35.079
They blow you up today,
you blow them up tomorrow.

01:45:35.788 --> 01:45:37.456
It's just business.

01:45:40.000 --> 01:45:41.210
You're wrong.

01:45:44.880 --> 01:45:45.923
Maybe.

01:45:49.635 --> 01:45:51.804
(KYLO REN GRUNTING)

01:45:55.099 --> 01:45:56.308
(REY GRUNTING)

01:45:58.727 --> 01:46:00.604
(REY STRAINING)

01:46:16.495 --> 01:46:18.122
- (LIGHTSABER BUZZING)
- (REY SHRIEKING)

01:46:32.177 --> 01:46:33.429
(LIGHTSABER CRACKLING)

01:47:13.928 --> 01:47:15.304
(STRUGGLING)

01:47:19.683 --> 01:47:21.185
(PANTING)

01:47:24.688 --> 01:47:26.190
(GRUNTING)

01:47:29.401 --> 01:47:30.402
REY: Ben!

01:47:42.665 --> 01:47:43.832
The fleet.

01:47:43.999 --> 01:47:45.000
Order them to stop firing.

01:47:45.167 --> 01:47:46.961
There's still time to save the fleet.

01:47:55.678 --> 01:47:56.762
Ben?

01:47:58.973 --> 01:48:00.933
It's time to let old things die.

01:48:03.477 --> 01:48:04.770
Snoke,

01:48:04.937 --> 01:48:06.188
Skywalker.

01:48:08.232 --> 01:48:09.608
The Sith,

01:48:10.275 --> 01:48:12.111
the Jedi, the Rebels...

01:48:12.277 --> 01:48:13.654
Let it all die.

01:48:14.279 --> 01:48:15.322
Rey.

01:48:17.366 --> 01:48:18.826
I want you to join me.

01:48:20.786 --> 01:48:23.372
We can rule together
and bring a new order to the galaxy.

01:48:23.539 --> 01:48:24.915
Don't do this, Ben.

01:48:26.083 --> 01:48:27.167
Please don't go this way.

01:48:27.334 --> 01:48:30.796
No, no. You're still
holding on! Let go!

01:48:31.964 --> 01:48:34.258
Do you wanna know the truth
about your parents?

01:48:35.259 --> 01:48:36.635
Or have you always known?

01:48:39.221 --> 01:48:40.806
And you've just hidden it away.

01:48:42.850 --> 01:48:44.351
You know the truth.

01:48:45.185 --> 01:48:46.645
Say it.

01:48:49.773 --> 01:48:50.983
Say it.

01:48:52.985 --> 01:48:54.528
They were nobody.

01:48:54.695 --> 01:48:56.321
They were filthy junk traders

01:48:56.488 --> 01:48:58.407
who sold you off for drinking money.

01:48:59.366 --> 01:49:00.367
(SOBS)

01:49:00.451 --> 01:49:03.579
They're dead in a paupers'
grave in the Jakku desert.

01:49:04.329 --> 01:49:06.290
You have no place in this story.

01:49:06.457 --> 01:49:08.459
You come from nothing.
You're nothing.

01:49:12.755 --> 01:49:14.048
But not to me.

01:49:18.135 --> 01:49:19.136
Join me.

01:49:32.608 --> 01:49:33.650
Please.

01:50:04.056 --> 01:50:05.057
Sir,

01:50:05.641 --> 01:50:08.393
the Resistance cruiser's
preparing to jump to lightspeed.

01:50:09.186 --> 01:50:10.270
It's empty.

01:50:10.437 --> 01:50:12.231
They're just trying
to pull our attention away.

01:50:12.731 --> 01:50:13.899
Pathetic.

01:50:14.066 --> 01:50:16.235
Keep your fire on the transports.

01:50:40.342 --> 01:50:42.261
(BOTH PANTING)

01:50:44.096 --> 01:50:46.807
PHASMA: Execution by blaster
is too good for them.

01:50:46.974 --> 01:50:49.017
Let's make this hurt.

01:50:54.731 --> 01:50:55.732
ROSE: Finn.

01:50:56.900 --> 01:50:57.901
(WEAPONS BUZZING)

01:51:00.362 --> 01:51:01.947
On my command.

01:51:06.743 --> 01:51:08.036
She's running away.

01:51:10.164 --> 01:51:11.331
No, she isn't.

01:51:16.879 --> 01:51:18.589
(INSTRUMENTS BEEPING)

01:51:25.220 --> 01:51:28.182
- No!
- Fire on that cruiser!

01:51:39.193 --> 01:51:40.194
(STRAINING)

01:51:40.903 --> 01:51:41.945
(GROANING)

01:51:42.029 --> 01:51:43.030
Execute.

01:52:24.404 --> 01:52:25.739
(ROSE GRUNTING)

01:52:27.157 --> 01:52:28.242
Finn!

01:52:28.408 --> 01:52:31.286
There's a shuttle back that way!
We gotta go!

01:52:46.677 --> 01:52:48.136
- Traitor!
- (BLASTER POWERING UP)

01:52:49.805 --> 01:52:50.806
What?

01:52:52.975 --> 01:52:54.434
(INDISTINCT SHOUTING)

01:53:06.530 --> 01:53:07.948
(BB-8 CHIRPING)

01:53:14.121 --> 01:53:15.122
Finn!

01:53:19.418 --> 01:53:20.627
(ROSE YELPS)

01:53:29.803 --> 01:53:31.054
(FINN SHOUTING)

01:53:34.516 --> 01:53:36.268
You are a bug in the system.

01:53:36.643 --> 01:53:37.853
Let's go, chrome dome.

01:53:40.022 --> 01:53:41.023
(FINN GRUNTING)

01:53:45.527 --> 01:53:46.653
Come on!

01:53:56.330 --> 01:53:57.331
No!

01:54:03.295 --> 01:54:04.296
Hey.

01:54:04.963 --> 01:54:05.964
(PHASMA GROANS)

01:54:20.228 --> 01:54:22.898
You were always scum.

01:54:24.441 --> 01:54:25.942
Rebel scum.

01:54:36.995 --> 01:54:37.996
(BB-8 CHIRPING)

01:54:39.456 --> 01:54:41.666
Hey! Need a lift?

01:55:19.454 --> 01:55:21.540
What happened?

01:55:22.165 --> 01:55:23.834
The girl murdered Snoke.

01:55:28.296 --> 01:55:29.631
What happened?

01:55:29.798 --> 01:55:32.342
She took Snoke's escape craft.

01:55:32.759 --> 01:55:34.177
We know where she's going.

01:55:35.178 --> 01:55:36.888
Get all our forces down
to that Resistance base.

01:55:37.347 --> 01:55:38.807
Let's finish this.

01:55:39.599 --> 01:55:40.767
Finish this?

01:55:41.351 --> 01:55:43.437
Who do you think you're talking to?

01:55:43.895 --> 01:55:46.398
You presume to command my army?

01:55:47.149 --> 01:55:50.527
Our Supreme Leader is dead!
We have no ruler!

01:55:50.652 --> 01:55:52.112
(CHOKING)

01:55:55.031 --> 01:55:58.368
The Supreme Leader is dead.

01:56:00.328 --> 01:56:03.457
Long live the Supreme Leader.

01:56:20.015 --> 01:56:21.183
(SPACECRAFT APPROACHING)

01:56:21.266 --> 01:56:23.435
They're coming, shut the door.

01:56:25.187 --> 01:56:26.396
(CREATURES WHIMPERING)

01:56:31.193 --> 01:56:32.861
Incoming!

01:56:36.490 --> 01:56:38.366
POE: Go! Go! Move!

01:56:39.326 --> 01:56:41.286
Get that shield door down!

01:56:43.205 --> 01:56:44.664
(INDISTINCT SHOUTING)

01:56:57.135 --> 01:56:58.428
ROSE: No! Wait, don't shoot! It's us!

01:56:58.512 --> 01:56:59.554
No! Don't shoot!

01:56:59.721 --> 01:57:00.722
Hold your fire!

01:57:00.889 --> 01:57:02.933
FINN: Don't shoot!
POE: Hold your fire!

01:57:05.477 --> 01:57:06.728
LEIA: Finn?
POE: Finn!

01:57:07.270 --> 01:57:08.939
Rose! You're not dead!

01:57:09.105 --> 01:57:10.315
Where's my droid?

01:57:10.398 --> 01:57:11.525
(BB-8 CHIRPING EXCITEDLY)

01:57:11.608 --> 01:57:12.651
Buddy!

01:57:12.817 --> 01:57:15.320
- I'm so glad to see you!
- (BB-8 CHIRPING HAPPILY)

01:57:16.738 --> 01:57:18.865
POE: Wait, what?
Wait, wait, wait, slow down.

01:57:19.032 --> 01:57:20.325
Is this all that's left?

01:57:30.669 --> 01:57:32.879
All right, shields are up
so they can't hit us from orbit.

01:57:33.213 --> 01:57:34.422
Use whatever power we've got left

01:57:34.589 --> 01:57:36.633
to broadcast a distress signal
to the Outer Rim.

01:57:36.800 --> 01:57:38.468
Use my personal code.

01:57:38.969 --> 01:57:41.805
If there are any allies to the Resistance,

01:57:42.347 --> 01:57:43.473
it's now or never.

01:57:44.182 --> 01:57:46.101
Rose, what do you got?

01:57:46.601 --> 01:57:50.188
Rotting munitions, rusted artillery,
some half-gutted skim speeders.

01:57:50.355 --> 01:57:51.356
Well,

01:57:52.357 --> 01:57:53.817
let's just pray that big-ass door

01:57:53.900 --> 01:57:56.194
holds long enough for us
to get help.

01:57:56.278 --> 01:57:57.362
(DISTANT RUMBLING)

01:57:57.445 --> 01:57:58.446
(CREATURES BARKING)

01:58:06.496 --> 01:58:08.290
FINN: A battering ram cannon.

01:58:08.456 --> 01:58:10.083
A what now?

01:58:10.500 --> 01:58:11.918
Miniaturized Death Star tech.

01:58:12.085 --> 01:58:13.837
It'll crack that door open like an egg.

01:58:14.588 --> 01:58:16.339
There has to be a back way
out of here, right?

01:58:16.423 --> 01:58:17.424
(BB-8 CHIRPING)

01:58:17.549 --> 01:58:19.342
POE: BB-8, what do you got?

01:58:20.176 --> 01:58:23.346
C-3PO: BB-8 has analyzed
the mine's schematics.

01:58:23.513 --> 01:58:26.641
This is the only way in or out.

01:58:26.725 --> 01:58:29.019
(DISTANT RUMBLING)

01:58:31.396 --> 01:58:32.856
(WALLS CREAKING)

01:58:33.982 --> 01:58:34.983
Come on.

01:58:35.984 --> 01:58:37.235
We have allies.

01:58:37.485 --> 01:58:39.321
People believe in Leia.

01:58:39.988 --> 01:58:41.573
They'll get our message, they'll come.

01:58:42.115 --> 01:58:44.367
But we have to buy time.

01:58:45.327 --> 01:58:47.996
We gotta take out that cannon.

01:58:52.292 --> 01:58:53.293
SOLDIER 1: On me! On me!

01:58:53.376 --> 01:58:54.377
(INDISTINCT SHOUTING)

01:58:54.461 --> 01:58:55.462
SOLDIER 2: Move! Move!

01:58:55.795 --> 01:58:57.172
Go back! Gather your weapons!

01:58:57.339 --> 01:58:58.757
SOLDIER 3: Get over here!

01:58:58.923 --> 01:58:59.924
SOLDIER 4: Hold your fire!

01:59:17.192 --> 01:59:18.193
Salt.

01:59:18.360 --> 01:59:19.653
SOLDIER 5: Ground forces, incoming.

01:59:19.819 --> 01:59:21.488
POE: (ON RADIO) Copy that. On our way.

01:59:38.880 --> 01:59:40.048
Engage your mono-ski.

01:59:40.215 --> 01:59:41.758
The green toggle.

01:59:43.551 --> 01:59:44.552
(GRUNTS)

01:59:51.810 --> 01:59:52.977
All right, listen up.

01:59:53.144 --> 01:59:56.272
I don't like these rust buckets
and I don't like our odds, but...

01:59:56.773 --> 01:59:58.066
What the hell?

01:59:58.233 --> 01:59:59.526
Just keep it tight

01:59:59.693 --> 02:00:02.654
and don't get drawn in too close
till they roll that cannon out front.

02:00:22.507 --> 02:00:24.759
All right, ground forces,
lay down some fire!

02:00:37.814 --> 02:00:39.691
Thirteen incoming light craft.

02:00:39.858 --> 02:00:41.776
Shall we hold until we clear them?

02:00:41.943 --> 02:00:44.821
No. The Resistance is in that mine.

02:00:45.363 --> 02:00:46.531
Push through.

02:00:51.369 --> 02:00:52.871
Fighters, break off!

02:01:02.964 --> 02:01:05.842
Come on! We gotta hold them
till they pull up that cannon!

02:01:08.887 --> 02:01:10.638
(SPEAKING ALIEN DIALECT)

02:01:11.473 --> 02:01:12.557
(SOLDIERS GROANING)

02:01:21.274 --> 02:01:23.318
Rose, you got three right behind you!

02:01:31.201 --> 02:01:32.202
I can't lose 'em!

02:01:39.334 --> 02:01:41.002
Whoo! Yeah!

02:01:45.381 --> 02:01:47.050
(CHEWIE GROWLS)

02:01:47.133 --> 02:01:49.385
(PORG GROWLS)

02:01:54.057 --> 02:01:56.017
Whoo! I like this!

02:02:04.609 --> 02:02:07.695
Blow that piece of junk out of the sky!

02:02:07.862 --> 02:02:09.239
All fighters!

02:02:16.412 --> 02:02:18.081
Chewie, peel off from the battle.

02:02:18.248 --> 02:02:19.582
Draw them away from the speeders.

02:02:19.791 --> 02:02:21.292
(CHEWIE GROWLS)

02:02:25.380 --> 02:02:27.048
She drew 'em off! All of 'em!

02:02:27.215 --> 02:02:28.800
Oh, they hate that ship!

02:02:35.932 --> 02:02:36.933
(PORG CHIRPING)

02:02:41.396 --> 02:02:42.397
Chewie!

02:02:42.605 --> 02:02:43.898
(CHEWIE GROWLS)

02:02:59.539 --> 02:03:00.540
(PORG CRYING)

02:03:00.665 --> 02:03:01.833
(CHEWIE GROWLS)

02:03:05.169 --> 02:03:06.713
(SCREAMS)

02:03:13.761 --> 02:03:14.762
There it is!

02:03:19.976 --> 02:03:21.060
That is a big gun.

02:03:21.227 --> 02:03:22.520
FINN: Okay, it's heavily armored.

02:03:22.687 --> 02:03:24.689
Our only shot is right down the throat.

02:03:32.488 --> 02:03:34.240
The cannon's opening. This is our chance.

02:03:34.407 --> 02:03:35.575
All firepower on those speeders.

02:03:35.742 --> 02:03:38.202
Concentrate all fire on the speeders!

02:03:45.084 --> 02:03:46.502
We're taking heavy losses.

02:03:46.586 --> 02:03:47.837
(INDISTINCT RADIO CHATTER)

02:03:52.383 --> 02:03:53.760
(SCREAMS)

02:03:56.554 --> 02:03:57.555
(YELPS)

02:03:58.932 --> 02:04:00.808
They're picking us all off.
We're not gonna make it.

02:04:00.975 --> 02:04:02.685
FINN: All right,
making my final approach.

02:04:02.852 --> 02:04:04.228
Target in sight, guns are hot.

02:04:04.395 --> 02:04:05.647
No! Pull off!

02:04:05.813 --> 02:04:06.856
What?

02:04:07.023 --> 02:04:08.441
The cannon is charged!
It's a suicide run!

02:04:08.608 --> 02:04:09.943
All craft, pull away!

02:04:10.109 --> 02:04:12.195
- No! I'm almost there!
- POE: Retreat, Finn!

02:04:12.362 --> 02:04:13.613
That's an order!

02:04:22.580 --> 02:04:24.749
Finn? It's too late! Don't do this!

02:04:24.916 --> 02:04:26.918
No! I won't let them win!

02:04:28.962 --> 02:04:30.922
No! Finn, listen to Poe!

02:04:31.089 --> 02:04:32.507
We have to retreat!

02:04:44.560 --> 02:04:46.980
MALE SCOUT: (ON RADIO)
The cannon is warming up now.

02:04:47.146 --> 02:04:48.356
MALE COMMANDER: (ON RADIO)
Copy that. We see it.

02:04:48.523 --> 02:04:50.274
MALE SCOUT: Preparing to fire.

02:05:01.119 --> 02:05:02.662
(SPEEDER RATTLING)

02:05:19.095 --> 02:05:20.096
(BLAST FIRING)

02:05:32.066 --> 02:05:33.901
Move! Go, go! Quick!

02:05:34.068 --> 02:05:35.778
SOLDIER 6: Let's go, let's go!

02:05:35.987 --> 02:05:38.031
(GRUNTING)

02:05:42.160 --> 02:05:43.369
Rose?

02:05:49.000 --> 02:05:50.126
Rose?

02:05:50.501 --> 02:05:51.919
Rose?

02:05:52.837 --> 02:05:54.672
Why would you do that? Huh?

02:05:54.756 --> 02:05:56.632
I was almost there.

02:05:57.425 --> 02:05:58.926
Why would you stop me?

02:05:59.677 --> 02:06:01.804
I saved you,

02:06:02.847 --> 02:06:03.848
dummy.

02:06:04.974 --> 02:06:06.642
That's how we're gonna win.

02:06:06.809 --> 02:06:09.187
Not fighting what we hate,

02:06:09.645 --> 02:06:11.981
saving what we love.

02:06:31.459 --> 02:06:32.794
KYLO REN: General Hux,

02:06:32.960 --> 02:06:34.504
advance.

02:06:34.962 --> 02:06:36.547
No quarter.

02:06:37.965 --> 02:06:39.509
No prisoners.

02:06:41.260 --> 02:06:44.514
Our distress signal's been
received at multiple points,

02:06:44.680 --> 02:06:46.766
but no response.

02:06:47.308 --> 02:06:49.060
They've heard us,

02:06:49.435 --> 02:06:51.562
but no one's coming.

02:06:55.900 --> 02:06:58.069
We fought till the end.

02:07:00.404 --> 02:07:05.368
But the galaxy has lost all its hope.

02:07:06.702 --> 02:07:08.162
The spark

02:07:10.081 --> 02:07:11.541
is out.

02:07:37.150 --> 02:07:38.734
Luke.

02:07:47.160 --> 02:07:49.745
I know what you're gonna say.

02:07:50.955 --> 02:07:52.790
I changed my hair.

02:07:54.792 --> 02:07:56.460
It's nice that way.

02:07:58.337 --> 02:07:59.964
Leia,

02:08:01.132 --> 02:08:02.133
I'm sorry.

02:08:02.300 --> 02:08:04.177
I know.

02:08:04.343 --> 02:08:06.554
I know you are.

02:08:07.346 --> 02:08:09.307
I'm just glad you're here

02:08:10.224 --> 02:08:11.809
at the end.

02:08:13.186 --> 02:08:15.021
I came to face him, Leia.

02:08:17.023 --> 02:08:19.275
And I can't save him.

02:08:19.650 --> 02:08:22.904
I held out hope for so long,

02:08:25.698 --> 02:08:28.242
but I know my son is gone.

02:08:29.118 --> 02:08:31.829
No one's ever really gone.

02:09:07.448 --> 02:09:09.283
C-3PO: Master Luke.

02:09:32.306 --> 02:09:33.307
Stop!

02:09:35.101 --> 02:09:36.477
(MACHINERY CREAKING)

02:09:58.958 --> 02:10:02.461
I want every gun we have
to fire on that man.

02:10:07.633 --> 02:10:09.135
Do it.

02:10:25.776 --> 02:10:26.861
More!

02:10:30.156 --> 02:10:31.157
More!

02:10:45.713 --> 02:10:47.340
That's enough.

02:10:48.799 --> 02:10:51.010
(SHOUTING) That's enough!

02:10:51.719 --> 02:10:53.262
(GUNS DEACTIVATING)

02:10:56.932 --> 02:10:58.559
Do you think you got him?

02:10:59.894 --> 02:11:01.729
Now, if we're ready to get moving,

02:11:01.896 --> 02:11:04.065
we can finish this.

02:11:04.231 --> 02:11:05.358
Sir?

02:11:27.880 --> 02:11:29.090
(EXHALES SHAKILY)

02:11:31.842 --> 02:11:33.177
Bring me down to him.

02:11:33.511 --> 02:11:36.347
Keep the door covered
and don't advance until I say.

02:11:36.430 --> 02:11:37.431
Supreme Leader,

02:11:37.890 --> 02:11:39.392
don't get distracted, our goal...

02:11:39.475 --> 02:11:40.559
(HUX YELPS)

02:11:41.894 --> 02:11:43.104
Right away, sir.

02:11:44.230 --> 02:11:45.773
Med pack!

02:11:45.940 --> 02:11:47.983
I need a med pack!

02:11:48.192 --> 02:11:50.236
She's hurt pretty bad.

02:12:09.004 --> 02:12:10.297
It's Kylo Ren.

02:12:10.464 --> 02:12:11.674
Luke's facing him alone.

02:12:11.841 --> 02:12:13.217
Well, we should help him. Let's go.

02:12:13.384 --> 02:12:15.094
No, wait. Wait.

02:12:29.024 --> 02:12:31.402
Did you come back to say you forgive me?

02:12:32.403 --> 02:12:34.280
To save my soul?

02:12:36.031 --> 02:12:37.658
No.

02:12:56.510 --> 02:12:58.762
He's doing this for a reason.

02:13:00.598 --> 02:13:02.349
He's stalling so we can escape.

02:13:02.433 --> 02:13:03.434
Escape?

02:13:03.517 --> 02:13:04.602
He's one man against an army.

02:13:04.685 --> 02:13:06.187
We have to help him,
we have to fight.

02:13:06.353 --> 02:13:08.564
No, no. We are the spark
that'll light the fire

02:13:08.647 --> 02:13:10.232
that'll burn the First Order down.

02:13:11.358 --> 02:13:14.445
Skywalker's doing this
so we can survive.

02:13:14.612 --> 02:13:16.071
There's gotta be a way
out of this mine.

02:13:16.155 --> 02:13:17.323
Hell, how did he get in here?

02:13:17.490 --> 02:13:21.535
Sir, it is possible that
a natural unmapped opening exists.

02:13:21.702 --> 02:13:24.663
But this facility is such
a maze of endless tunnels

02:13:24.830 --> 02:13:26.540
that the odds of finding an exit

02:13:26.624 --> 02:13:29.335
- are 15,428...
- Shh. Shush. Hush. Shush up.

02:13:29.418 --> 02:13:30.961
Shut up!

02:13:32.171 --> 02:13:33.881
- To one.
- Listen.

02:13:36.550 --> 02:13:38.802
C-3PO: My audio sensors
no longer detect the...

02:13:38.969 --> 02:13:40.054
POE: Exactly.

02:13:45.935 --> 02:13:48.646
Where'd the crystal critters go?

02:13:49.313 --> 02:13:50.814
(CREATURE WHIMPERING)

02:13:54.318 --> 02:13:55.319
Follow me.

02:13:59.865 --> 02:14:01.825
What are you looking at me for?

02:14:01.992 --> 02:14:03.494
Follow him.

02:14:12.920 --> 02:14:14.338
(BEACON PULSATING RAPIDLY)

02:14:15.130 --> 02:14:17.591
If the beacon's right beneath us,
they've got to be somewhere.

02:14:17.758 --> 02:14:19.260
Keep scanning for life forms.

02:14:19.343 --> 02:14:21.136
(BEACON PULSATING RAPIDLY)

02:14:29.061 --> 02:14:30.604
This way.

02:14:32.898 --> 02:14:34.942
(PORG CHITTERING)

02:14:35.150 --> 02:14:36.819
I see them! Chewie, there!

02:14:39.280 --> 02:14:41.073
(CREATURES YIPPING)

02:14:48.455 --> 02:14:50.249
(CREATURE WHINING)

02:14:50.499 --> 02:14:53.377
No. No, no, no.

02:14:56.755 --> 02:14:57.756
No!

02:15:04.471 --> 02:15:06.265
(CREATURES BARKING)

02:15:10.019 --> 02:15:11.854
Lifting rocks.

02:15:12.354 --> 02:15:13.564
(BREATHING HEAVILY)

02:15:24.325 --> 02:15:26.368
(KYLO REN GRUNTING)

02:15:35.377 --> 02:15:37.212
(LIGHTSABER CRACKLING)

02:15:46.805 --> 02:15:47.806
(GRUNTING)

02:15:51.935 --> 02:15:54.438
I failed you, Ben.

02:15:55.272 --> 02:15:57.650
- I'm sorry.
- I'm sure you are!

02:15:58.817 --> 02:16:00.861
The Resistance is dead.

02:16:01.028 --> 02:16:02.613
The war is over.

02:16:02.780 --> 02:16:04.782
And when I kill you,

02:16:04.948 --> 02:16:07.409
I will have killed the last Jedi.

02:16:07.576 --> 02:16:08.661
Amazing.

02:16:09.244 --> 02:16:12.998
Every word of what you just said
was wrong.

02:16:15.376 --> 02:16:18.462
The Rebellion is reborn today.

02:16:20.673 --> 02:16:22.675
The war

02:16:22.841 --> 02:16:24.510
is just beginning.

02:16:25.719 --> 02:16:29.598
And I will not be the last Jedi.

02:17:09.388 --> 02:17:11.432
I'll destroy her,

02:17:11.598 --> 02:17:13.642
and you,

02:17:13.809 --> 02:17:15.436
and all of it.

02:17:19.273 --> 02:17:20.274
No.

02:17:21.400 --> 02:17:24.653
Strike me down in anger
and I'll always be with you.

02:17:27.281 --> 02:17:29.366
Just like your father.

02:17:35.873 --> 02:17:37.624
(LIGHTSABER CRACKLING)

02:17:40.002 --> 02:17:41.003
(GRUNTS)

02:17:42.045 --> 02:17:43.756
(SCREAMING)

02:18:18.791 --> 02:18:19.792
No.

02:18:24.129 --> 02:18:26.256
See you around, kid.

02:18:39.937 --> 02:18:41.313
No!

02:18:59.164 --> 02:19:00.165
(GRUNTS)

02:20:56.365 --> 02:20:57.824
(DOOR CLOSING)

02:21:18.762 --> 02:21:20.806
- (C'AI LAUGHS)
- C'ai!

02:21:20.889 --> 02:21:22.849
- C-3PO: Such a friend.
- (R2-D2 BLEEPS)

02:21:23.183 --> 02:21:24.935
- (CHEWIE GROWLS)
- Chewie!

02:21:25.018 --> 02:21:26.144
(BB-8 CHIRPS INQUISITIVELY)

02:21:26.228 --> 02:21:27.980
- It looks good.
- (BB-8 CHIRPS)

02:21:28.438 --> 02:21:29.606
CONNIX: That was crazy, man.

02:21:31.024 --> 02:21:32.526
- POE: Hi.
- Hi.

02:21:33.110 --> 02:21:34.152
I'm Poe.

02:21:34.987 --> 02:21:35.988
Rey.

02:21:36.363 --> 02:21:37.406
I know.

02:21:49.710 --> 02:21:51.712
D'ACY: When we get to the Outer Rim,
I have a contact there.

02:21:51.795 --> 02:21:53.046
C-3PO: Quite definitely possible.

02:22:03.515 --> 02:22:05.017
Luke is gone.

02:22:05.892 --> 02:22:07.269
I felt it.

02:22:07.894 --> 02:22:09.730
But it wasn't sadness or pain.

02:22:10.981 --> 02:22:13.316
It was peace and purpose.

02:22:14.276 --> 02:22:15.610
I felt it, too.

02:22:18.280 --> 02:22:21.199
How do we build a Rebellion from this?

02:22:25.620 --> 02:22:28.373
We have everything we need.

02:22:30.500 --> 02:22:32.002
(BB-8 CHIRPS)

02:22:39.342 --> 02:22:41.470
(SPEAKING ALIEN DIALECT)

02:22:48.018 --> 02:22:49.811
Luke Skywalker,

02:22:49.978 --> 02:22:51.772
Jedi Master.

02:22:51.897 --> 02:22:53.148
(SPEAKING ALIEN DIALECT)

02:22:54.983 --> 02:22:56.526
(ROARS)

02:22:57.486 --> 02:22:58.820
(SPEAKING ALIEN DIALECT)

02:23:39.861 --> 02:23:41.905
(THEME MUSIC PLAYING)

